%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tony%20Bennett%3A%20Legendary%20singer%20dies%20aged%2096%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689943666000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F83B3%2Fproduction%2F_115651733_breaking-large-promo-nc.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66271090%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tony%20Bennett%2C%20legendary%20singer%20who%20duetted%20with%20Aretha%20Franklin%20and%20Lady%20Gaga%2C%20dies%20aged%2096.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66271090%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66271090.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fentertainment-arts-66271090.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Manipur%20Video%3A%20What%20Connects%203%20Kuki%20Women%20Stripped%2C%20Paraded%20Naked%20to%20Manorama%20and%20Bilkis%20Bano%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21180403%2Fimage-1162.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20nights%20ago%2C%20coming%20out%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98no%20connectivity%E2%80%99%20zone%20in%20a%20remote%20part%20of%20Ladakh%2C%20what%20my%20phone%20feed%20flashed%20was%20a%20video%20already%20viral%20%E2%80%93%20two%20terrified%20Kuki%20women%2C%20paraded%20naked%20and%20sexually%20abused%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20Meitei%20men%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20WhatsApp%2C%20I%20found%20several%20groups%20from%20across%20the%20Northeast%20where%20the%20video%20was%20already%20the%20major%20point%20of%20discussion.%20What%20stood%20out%20as%20a%20common%20strain%20in%20all%20of%20those%20chats%20was%3A%20%3Cem%3EHow%20could%20our%20men%20do%20this%20to%20our%20women%3F%20Is%20this%20our%20Northeast%3F%20Are%20these%20our%20men%3F%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Instagram%2C%20a%20prominent%20Assamese%20who%20organises%20a%20Northeast%20festival%20in%20New%20Delhi%20and%20elsewhere%20commented%3A%20%E2%80%9CDisgusting.%20Manipur%2C%20you%20have%20let%20all%20of%20us%20(read%20Northeasterner)%20down.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Twitter%2C%20the%20first%20post%20that%20popped%20up%20on%20my%20screen%20was%20from%20a%20young%20politician%20and%20former%20student%20leader%20of%20Assam%2C%20Luringjyoti%20Gogoi.%20%E2%80%9CAlways%20used%20to%20take%20pride%20in%20the%20level%20of%20respect%20for%20women%20in%20the%20Northeast.%20Yesterday%E2%80%99s%20video%20from%20Manipur%20has%20shattered%20and%20devastated%20me%E2%80%A6Are%20we%20allowing%20ourselves%20to%20become%20animals%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20tweeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20million%20thoughts%20swirled%20in%20my%20head%20even%20as%20I%20was%20struggling%20to%20swallow%20the%20harrowing%20details%20now%20overtaking%20my%20timeline.%20So%20much%20was%20tumbling%20out%20of%20Manipur%20on%20my%20digital%20feed%2C%20from%20a%20state%20badly%20battered%20due%20to%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20between%20two%20communities%20for%20nearly%20three%20months%20now%20%E2%80%93%20completely%20abandoned%20by%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20double%20engine%2C%20having%20just%20succeeded%20in%20grinding%20down%20and%20trivialising%20the%20horror%2C%20has%20no%20route%20map%20for%20redress%20or%20peace.%20I%20particularly%20recalled%20writing%20down%20in%20my%20notepad%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3Ewhat%20two%20distressed%20fathers%20from%20a%20Kuki%20village%20in%20Kangpokpi%20district%20had%20told%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20the%20telephone%20on%20May%2029.%20Their%20daughters%20were%20killed%20at%20their%20place%20of%20work%20in%20Imphal%20on%20May%205.%20Their%20fathers%20said%20they%20suspected%20their%20girls%20were%20raped%20before%20they%20were%20murdered%20but%20there%20was%20no%20way%20to%20confirm%20it%2C%20since%20they%20feared%20travelling%20to%20the%20Meitei-dominated%20Imphal%20to%20claim%20the%20bodies%20kept%20at%20the%20morgue%20of%20a%20government-run%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhen%20did%20such%20horror%20unfold%20before%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20May%204%20video%20also%20made%20me%20wonder%2C%20when%20was%20it%20last%20that%20such%20a%20horrifying%20episode%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20of%20women%20had%20been%20documented%20in%20my%20region%20during%20an%20ethnic%20fight%20between%20two%20communities%3F%20Gradually%2C%20a%20canvas%20emerged%3B%20things%20fell%20in%20place%2C%20aided%20principally%20by%20some%20key%20words%20that%20had%20appeared%20in%20those%20shocked%20reactions%20I%20had%20soaked%20in%20on%20social%20media%20from%20across%20the%20Northeast%20on%20the%20brutality%20and%20shamelessness%20of%20a%20bunch%20of%20men%20from%20within%20the%20region.%20Those%20key%20words%20were%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eus%2C%20our%2C%20we.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEthnic%20conflict%20is%20not%20new%20to%20Manipur%20and%20to%20the%20Northeast%20in%20general.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20tribe%2Fcommunity%20burning%20down%20another%E2%80%99s%20property%20is%20not%20new%20either%20%E2%80%93%20rather%20it%E2%80%99s%20seen%20as%20a%20pattern.%20Killings%20too%20are%20not%20new%2C%20unfortunately%3B%20a%20disturbing%20fact.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20also%20reckoned%20that%20cases%20of%20rape%20and%20sexual%20assault%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20long-drawn%20out%20militancy-affected%20Northeast%20%E2%80%93%20have%20more%20often%20than%20not%20been%20examples%20of%20our%20women%20violated%20by%20%3Cem%3Etheir%20%3C%2Fem%3Emen.%20%3Cem%3ETheir%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20here%2C%20means%20the%20face%20of%20the%20state%20on%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%93%20the%20security%20forces%2C%20men%20who%20typically%20belonged%20to%20the%20mainland%2C%20accused%20of%20sexually%20assaulting%20women%20from%20the%20region%20often%20under%20the%20protection%20of%20the%20Armed%20Forces%20(Special)%20Powers%20Act%20(AFSPA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20knock%20at%20the%20door%20in%202000%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMy%20mind%20sharply%20recalled%20the%20night%20of%20June%2013%2C%202000.%20A%20knock%20at%20the%20door%20of%20Naruttom%20Haloi%20(name%20changed)%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Assam%E2%80%99s%20Nalbari%20district%2C%20preceded%20a%20harrowing%20time%20for%20his%20family.%20A%20group%20of%20Army%20jawans%20had%20surrounded%20their%20modest%20house.%20No%20sooner%20did%20Haloi%20open%20the%20door%2C%20heavy%20boots%20barged%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaloi%20lived%20with%20two%20wives.%20The%20first%20wife%20and%20he%20were%20badly%20beaten%2C%20and%20then%20pushed%20out%20of%20the%20house.%20The%20jawans%2C%20thereafter%2C%20dragged%20a%20frightened%20second%20wife%20from%20under%20a%20bed%20and%20allegedly%20gangraped%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaloi%20and%20his%20first%20wife%20screamed%20for%20help%3B%20villagers%20came%3B%20the%20jawans%20fled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Assam-based%20Manav%20Adhikar%20Sangram%20Samiti%20(MASS)%2C%20which%20later%20documented%20the%20case%20based%20on%20the%20victim%20and%20witness%20testimonials%2C%20Haloi%20took%20his%20second%20wife%20to%20the%20nearest%20army%20camp%20the%20next%20morning%20to%20complain%20to%20the%20officer%20in%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officer%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Haloi%20family%E2%80%99s%20testimony%20to%20MASS%2C%20handed%20them%20Rs%20200%20and%20five%20kilograms%20of%20rice.%20In%20a%20state%20with%20AFSPA%20at%20play%2C%20that%20generosity%20of%20the%20man%20in%20uniform%20came%20laced%20with%20sharp%20advice%20%E2%80%93%20do%20not%20speak%20of%20the%20incident%20to%20anyone.%20The%20scared%20duo%20trod%20back%20home%2C%20and%20never%20filed%20a%20police%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHeinous%20crimes%20like%20this%20one%20that%20took%20place%2023%20years%20ago%20in%20Assam%2C%20and%20the%20one%20in%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Kangpokpi%20district%20recorded%20on%20May%204%2C%20have%20a%20parallel%20%E2%80%93%20they%20can%20never%20be%20documented%20fully%20without%20taking%20into%20cognisance%20the%20patriarchal%20pull%20and%20push%20of%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%2C%20and%20therefore%20the%20right%20over%20their%20bodies%20against%20their%20will.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20humid%20day%20in%20Nalbari%2C%20the%20army%20officer%20who%20could%20most%20likely%20offer%20that%20appalling%20advice%20to%20the%20hapless%20rape%20survivor%20seeking%20justice%20from%20him%20only%20because%20she%20was%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20forget%20a%20fundamental%20thought%20that%20must%20have%20driven%20the%20perpetrators%20residing%20in%20that%20village%20in%20Nalbari%20district%20for%20some%20time%20to%20target%20the%20victim%20%E2%80%93%20she%20was%20Haloi%E2%80%99s%20second%20wife%2C%20and%20that%20information%20might%20have%20been%20key%3B%20she%20was%20no%20%E2%80%98Sati%20Savitri%E2%80%99%20after%20all.%20Only%20%E2%80%98Sati%20Savitris%2C%E2%80%99%20as%20per%20an%20Indian%20male-controlled%20society%2C%20have%20a%20right%20to%20dignity%2C%20right%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fkuki-woman-from-viral-video-speaks-out-on-sexual-assault-witnessing-murders%5C%22%3EKuki%20Woman%20From%20Viral%20Video%20Speaks%20Out%20on%20Sexual%20Assault%2C%20Witnessing%20Murders%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERevenge%2C%20retribution%20and%20a%20vicious%20cycle%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Manipur%20on%20May%204%2C%20as%20per%20the%20testimonials%20of%20the%20survivors%2C%20the%20Meitei%20men%20told%20them%20%E2%80%93%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewomen%20were%20raped%20by%20%3Cem%3Eyour%3C%2Fem%3E%20men%20in%20Churachandpur%20(that%20contention%20was%20based%20on%20a%20fake%20video).%20Therefore%2C%20their%20women%20were%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20through%20their%20bodies.%20Case%20after%20case%20of%20sexual%20abuse%20in%20conflict%20zones%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20state%20immunity%20have%20also%20held%20up%20that%20the%20same%20rule%20could%20be%20operative%20%E2%80%93%20their%20women%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20a%20price%20with%20their%20bodies%20for%20their%20men%E2%80%99s%20fault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20years%20after%20that%20wretched%20Nalbari%20case%2C%20on%20another%20humid%20summer%20day%2C%20in%20neighbouring%20Manipur%20%E2%80%93%20also%20under%20AFSPA%20then%20%E2%80%93%20Thangjam%20Manorama%20was%20allegedly%20raped%2C%20brutally%20tortured%20and%20killed%20by%20an%20Assam%20Rifles%20team.%20Let%E2%80%99s%20also%20not%20allow%20ourselves%20here%20to%20ignore%20the%20thought%20that%20Manorama%20went%20through%20what%20she%20did%20also%20because%20she%20was%20being%20made%20to%20pay%20the%20price%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewoman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELet%E2%80%99s%20also%20reckon%20here%20that%20the%20horrifying%20Manorama%20case%20from%20July%202004%20gave%20independent%20India%20the%20most%20powerful%2C%20and%20distressing%2C%20symbol%20of%20women%E2%80%99s%20resistance%20to%20state-sponsored%20rape%20%E2%80%93%20around%2030%20middle-aged%20Meitei%20women%20who%20belonged%20to%20Manorama%E2%80%99s%20community%20stripped%20naked%20in%20front%20of%20the%20citadel%20of%20their%20honour%2C%20the%20Kangla%20Fort%20standing%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%2C%20to%20protest%20the%20sexual%20abuse.%20That%20incident%20made%20the%20country%20note%20with%20shock%20and%20horror%20what%20was%20happening%20to%20women%20in%20Manipur%20then%20%E2%80%93%20only%20to%20be%20replaced%20on%20another%20July%20day%2C%20nearly%2020%20years%20later%2C%20by%20yet%20another%20horrifying%20sight%20of%20what%20a%20set%20of%20women%20from%20that%20state%20had%20to%20undergo%20during%20another%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fwomen-of-the-northeast-present-a-picture-of-contrasts%5C%22%3EWomen%20of%20the%20Northeast%20Present%20a%20Picture%20of%20Contrasts%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPM%20speaks.%20And%20he%20does%20not.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20the%20perpetrators%20were%20Meitei%20men.%20The%20gaze%20of%20the%20perpetrators%20in%20both%20the%20crimes%2C%20let%E2%80%99s%20acknowledge%2C%20has%20not%20altered%20%E2%80%93%20like%20Manorama%20was%20seen%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman%20by%20her%20perpetrators%2C%20the%20Kuki%20women%20were%20also%20looked%20at%20as%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%20by%20the%20Meitei%20mob.%20It%20gave%20both%20sets%20of%20culprits%20the%20license%20to%20sexually%20assault%20a%20woman%20during%20a%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20May%204%20video%20kicking%20up%20nationwide%20outrage%2C%20finally%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fseventy-nine-days-after-violence-broke-out-narendra-modi-finally-talks-about-manipur%5C%22%3Ewas%20forced%20to%20break%20his%20silence%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Manipur.%20That%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20speak%20about%20those%20survivors%20inside%20the%20temple%20of%20our%20democracy%2C%20the%20Parliament%2C%20as%20the%20norm%20is%2C%20but%20outside%20it%2C%20and%20also%20not%20without%20attacking%20opposition-ruled%20states%2C%20may%20be%20overlooked%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20focusing%20on%20what%20he%20said.%20After%20all%2C%20absorbing%20the%20string%20of%20sentences%20%E2%80%93%20spoken%20post%20a%20deathly%2C%20unprecedented%20silence%20over%20nearly%20three%20months%20%E2%80%93%20must%20take%20precedence%20over%20propriety.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20too%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20male-controlled%20gaze%20of%20%3Cem%3Eour%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%20could%20be%20spotted.%20Modi%20rightly%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Csorrow%20and%20anger%E2%80%9D%20at%20the%20incident%3B%20he%20called%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20shameful%20act%E2%80%9D.%20But%20the%20most%20operational%20part%20of%20that%20short%20speech%20spoken%20in%20front%20of%20a%20battery%20of%20TV%20cameras%20was%20this%20%E2%80%93%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20has%20happened%20to%20the%20daughters%20of%20Manipur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fmanipur-sc-steps-in-pm-breaks-silence-opp-wants-his-statement-in-parliament-8851376%2F%5C%22%3Ecan%20never%20be%20forgiven%3C%2Fa%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20he%20expressed%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20over%20the%20survivors%20%E2%80%93%20as%20%3Cem%3Eour%3C%2Fem%3E%20women%2C%20%3Cem%3Eour%20%3C%2Fem%3Edaughters%20whose%20perpetrators%20must%20be%20punished.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBilkis%20Bano%20redux%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarely%20nine%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fbilkis-bano-husband-convict-release%5C%22%3Eokayed%20the%20release%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20as%20many%20as%2011%20convicted%20rapists%20in%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20home%20minister%E2%80%99s%20home%20state%20of%20Gujarat.%20When%20you%20juxtapose%20his%20July%2020%20speech%20against%20that%20October%202022%20decision%2C%20you%20are%20left%20wondering%2C%20what%20must%20be%20the%20reason%20for%20Modi%20choosing%20to%20be%20the%20first%20Indian%20prime%20minster%20to%20support%20a%20set%20of%20convicted%20rapists%20being%20released%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20it%20%3Cem%3Etheir%3C%2Fem%3E%20woman%20at%20play%20then%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWas%20Bilkis%20Bano%20%3Cem%3Etheirs%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%