ponse%20to%20a%20question%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20by%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20MPs%20Ravindra%20Kushwaha%20and%20Khagen%20Murmu%2C%20on%20Friday%2C%20July%2021.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20MPs%20asked%20whether%20the%20number%20of%20people%20dying%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmyocarditis-covid-19-heart-disease-vaccine%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecardiac%20attacks%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20have%20increased%20across%20the%20country%20after%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20the%20health%20minister%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CSudden%20deaths%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20some%20youth%20after%20COVID-19.%20However%2C%20at%20present%20sufficient%20evidence%20is%20not%20available%20to%20confirm%20the%20cause%20of%20such%20deaths.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20minister%20added%20that%20in%20order%20to%20ascertain%20the%20facts%20regarding%20the%20apprehension%20of%20rising%20cases%20of%20cardiac%20arrest%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20(ICMR)%20is%20conducting%20three%20studies.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20first%20of%20the%20studies%20aims%20to%20look%20at%20the%20%E2%80%98factors%20associated%20with%20sudden%20deaths%20among%20adults%20aged%2018%20to%2045%20years%E2%80%99%20in%20India.%20This%20is%20a%20multi-centric%20matched%20case%20control%20study%2C%20a%20type%20of%20observational%20exercise%20where%20groups%20are%20compared%20on%20various%20parameters.%20Mandaviya%20said%20this%20study%20is%20afoot%20at%20around%2040%20hospitals%20and%20research%20centres.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20second%20study%20is%20looking%20at%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20on%20thrombotic%20events%20among%2018%20to%2045-year-old%20people%20in%20India.%20This%20too%20is%20a%20multi-centric%2C%20hospital%20based%2C%20matched%20case%20control%20study.%20The%20health%20minister%20said%20this%20is%20ongoing%20at%20around%2030%20COVID-19%20clinical%20registry%20hospitals.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnalyses%C2%A0had%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fhealth%2Fmyocarditis-covid-19-heart-disease-vaccine%2F%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20situations%20like%20Myocarditis%20following%20COVID-19%20vaccination%20is%20rare%2C%20the%20risk%20is%20much%20smaller%20than%20the%20risks%20of%20cardiac%20injury%20linked%20to%20COVID-19%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20a%20third%20study%20is%20titled%20%E2%80%98Establishing%20the%20cause%20in%20sudden%20unexplained%20death%20in%20the%20young%2C%E2%80%99%20and%20is%20being%20done%20through%20virtual%20and%20physical%20autopsies%2C%20Mandaviya%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20in%20order%20to%20address%20the%20health%20issues%20related%20to%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20the%20his%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20provides%20technical%20and%20financial%20support%20to%20the%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20under%20the%20National%20Programme%20for%20Prevention%20and%20Control%20of%20Non-Communicable%20Diseases%20(NP%20NCD).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CCardiovascular%20Disease%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20NP%20NCD%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20months%2C%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20an%20unusual%20increase%20in%20sudden%20cardiac%20deaths%20in%20apparently%20healthy%20individuals%20who%20had%20a%20history%20of%20COVID-19.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ERakesh%20Yadav%2C%20professor%20at%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Studies%20(AIIMS)%20had%20said%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fdelhi%2Fcovid-link-in-cardiac-deaths-among-youths%2Farticleshow%2F98460423.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cem%3ETimes%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20March%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20while%20there%20is%20no%20quantifiable%20data%2C%20anecdotal%20evidence%20suggested%20an%20increase%20of%2010-15%25%20in%20such%20cases.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESome%20studies%20have%20pointed%20to%20the%20increased%20risk%20of%20cardiovascular%20diseases%20after%20COVID.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20study%20titled%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nature.com%2Farticles%2Fs41591-022-01689-3%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%98Long-term%20cardiovascular%20outcomes%20of%20COVID-19%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20published%20in%20the%20journal%20%3Cem%3ENature%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20concluded%20that%20the%20risk%20and%20one-year%20burden%20of%20cardiovascular%20disease%20in%20survivors%20of%20acute%20COVID-19%20are%20substantial.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20no%20large-scale%20studies%20on%20increased%20number%20of%20cardiac%20deaths%20especially%20among%20youths%20in%20India%2C%20although%20a%20few%20hospitals%20have%20carried%20out%20such%20studies%20their%20own.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ICMR%20said%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.moneycontrol.com%2Fnews%2Ftrends%2Fhealth%2Fexclusive-icmr-reviewing-preliminary-findings-on-link-between-covid-jabs-and-sudden-heart-attack-deaths-dg-rajiv-bahl-10824041.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elast%20month%20to%20%3Cem%3EMoneycontrol%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20results%20of%20its%20study%20into%20heart%20attacks%20in%20young%20individuals%20%3C%2Fspan%3Epost-COVID%2C%20and%20their%20plausible%20reasons%20will%20be%20made%20public%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689942608000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F01%2F12105819%2F2022_1img11_Jan_2022_PTI01_11_2022_000055B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%