e%20India%20should%20adopt.%20In%20this%20model%2C%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20acts%20in%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20all%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20shareholders%2C%20employees%2C%20and%20staff.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20being%20associated%20with%20the%20%E2%80%9CRaja%E2%80%9D%20model%20as%20his%20family%20bears%20the%20name%20of%20the%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%2C%20Uday%20Kotak%20seemingly%20supports%20the%20adoption%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9CCustodian%E2%80%9D%20model%20by%20the%20board%20of%20directors%20at%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20lack%20of%20any%20commentary%20on%20such%20a%20critical%20issue%20casts%20doubts%20over%20what%20the%20bank%20says%20about%C2%A0adhering%20to%20the%20%E2%80%9Chighest%20standards%20of%20corporate%20governance%20which%20includes%20disclosure%2C%20transparency%20and%20responsiveness%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20board%2C%20chaired%20by%20Prakash%20Apte%2C%20along%20with%20the%20executive%20leadership%20of%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20chief%20executive%20officer%20(CEO)%20Uday%20Kotak%2C%20and%20Dipak%20Gupta%2C%20appears%20unwilling%20to%20acknowledge%20this%20issue%20to%20the%20shareholders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUday%20Kotak%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fuday-kotak-kotak-mahindra-bank-ceo-new-role-non-independent-director-11682141557964.html%5C%22%3Ewill%20take%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20role%20of%20a%20non-executive%2C%20non-independent%20director%20of%20the%20bank%20after%20his%20tenure%20as%20the%20CEO%20ends%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20evident%20from%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%E2%80%99s%20(KMB)w%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.kotak.com%2Fcontent%2Fdam%2FKotak%2Finvestor-relation%2FFinancial-Result%2FAnnual-Reports%2FFY-2023%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank%2Fkotak-mahindra-bank-limited-FY22-23.pdf%5C%22%3Eannual%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20the%20financial%20year%202023%20which%20portrays%20the%20bank%E2%80%99s%20overt%20commitment%20to%20