p%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKMB%E2%80%99s%20proud%20proclamations%20that%20it%20follows%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20corporate%20governance%2C%20transparency%20and%20accountability%20carries%20little%20credibility%20when%20its%20board%20remains%20silent%20about%20such%20massive%20employee%20exits.%20The%20issue%20requires%20intervention%20by%20the%20regulator%20before%20a%20major%20disruption%20occurs%20in%20the%20bank.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20questionnaire%20was%20sent%20to%20Kotak%20Mahindra%20Bank%20on%20July%2016%20but%20despite%20reminders%20the%20bank%20has%20declined%20to%20respond%20till%20the%20time%20of%20going%20to%20press.%20The%20story%20will%20be%20updated%20if%20and%20when%20the%20bank%20sends%20a%20response%20to%20the%20queries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHemindra%20Hazari%2C%20is%20a%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Board%20of%20India%20(SEBI)-registered%20independent%20research%20analyst.%20He%20owns%C2%A0equity%20shares%20in%20all%20the%20banks%20mentioned%20in%20this%20report.%20HDFC%20Bank%20subscribes%20to%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20research%20and%20a%20member%20of%20this%20analyst%E2%80%99s%20family%20is%20employed%20with%20HDFC%20Bank.%20Views%20expressed%20are%20personal.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDisclaimer%3A%20This%20Insight%20does%20not%20contain%20and%20is%20not%20based%20on%20any%20non-public%2C%20material%20information.%20To%20the%20best%20of%20my%20knowledge%2C%20the%20views%20expressed%20in%20this%20Insight%20comply%20with%20Indian%20law%20as%20well%20as%20applicable%20law%20in%20the%20country%20from%20which%20it%20is%20posted.%20I%20have%20not%20been%20commissioned%20to%20write%20this%20Insight%20or%20hold%20any%20specific%20opinion%20on%20the%20securities%20referenced%20therein.%20This%20Insight%20is%20for%20informational%20purposes%20only%20and%20is%20not%20intended%20to%20provide%20financial%2C%20investment%20or%20other%20professional%20advice.%20It%20should%20not%20be%20construed%20as%20an%20offer%20to%20sell%2C%20a%