order%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20challenged%20in%20higher%20courts.%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20last%20year%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshivling-found-in-the-gyanvapi-mosque-will-be-protected-until-further-orders-says-supreme-court-extending-may-ruling-3511268%5C%22%3Edirected%20the%20sealing%20of%20the%20'wazukhana'%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20informed%20that%20my%20application%20has%20been%20approved%20and%20the%20court%20has%20directed%20to%20conduct%20an%20ASI%20survey%20of%20the%20Gyanvapi%20mosque%20complex%2C%20excluding%20the%20Wazu%20tank%20which%20has%20been%20sealed%2C%26quot%3B%20Vishnu%20Shankar%20Jain%2C%20representing%20the%20petitioners%20in%20the%20case%2C%20said%2C%20according%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20was%20moved%20in%20May%20this%20year%20by%20four%20women%20worshippers%2C%20who%20claimed%20the%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%2C%20located%20next%20to%20the%20Kashi%20Vishwanath%20temple%2C%20had%20signs%20of%20an%20ancient%20Hindu%20temple.%C2%A0The%20application%20stated%20that%20%3Cem%3ESwayambhu%20Jyotirlinga%3C%2Fem%3E%20existed%20at%20the%20site%20for%20lakhs%20of%20years%2C%20however%2C%20the%20same%20was%20destroyed%2Fdamaged%20several%20times%20by%20%26quot%3BMuslim%20Invaders%20who%20had%20hatred%20against%20infidels%20and%20idol%20worshippers%20beginning%20with%20the%20attack%20of%20Mahmud%20Ghazni%20in%201017%20AD%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20application%20further%20states%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20fanatic%20and%20cruel%20Mughal%20Emperors%2C%20Aurangzeb%26quot%3B%20issued%20%3Cem%3EFarman%20%3C%2Fem%3E(decree)%20in%201669%20to%20demolish%20the%20Temple%20of%20Lord%20Adivisheshwar%20at%20the%20site%20in%20question%20and%20in%20pursuance%20of%20his%20command%2C%20his%20subordinates%20carried%20out%20the%20order%20by%20demolishing%20the%20aforesaid%20Temple.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Jain%20earlier%20said%20he%20arg