0the%20development%20of%20Delhi%20as%20a%20major%20city.%20Its%20floodplains%20helped%20with%20agriculture%20and%20people%20started%20settling%20in%20the%20areas%20adjoining%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201930s%2C%20the%20land%20was%20leased%20for%20collective%20cropping%20and%20grazing%20by%20the%20British%20controlled%20Delhi%20Improvement%20Trust%20%E2%80%93%20a%20precursor%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0to%20the%20farmers%20of%20the%20area.%20After%20the%20DDA%20was%20constituted%2C%20it%20claimed%20ownership%20of%20the%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20Delhi%20Development%20Plan%20declares%20the%20flood%20plain%20area%20as%20ecologically%20sensitive.%20A%20plan%20to%20build%20a%20biodiversity%20park%20is%20in%20place%2C%20but%20flyovers%20and%20other%20concrete%20constructions%20have%20damaged%20the%20sensitive%20ecology%20of%20the%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20DUSIB%20Act%2C%20the%20government%20can%20only%20demolish%20already%20existing%20unauthorised%20%3Cem%3Ejhuggi%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ejhopadis%3C%2Fem%3E%20only%20after%20providing%20rehabilitation%20for%20the%20people%20staying%20there.%20But%20in%20case%20of%20Bela%20estate%2C%20no%20rehabilitation%20was%20done%2C%20which%20left%20people%20who%20had%20already%20been%20displaced%20as%20part%20of%20G20%20beautification%20drives%2C%20with%20no%20homes%20during%20the%20floods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2F1JyOLHiYusE%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689938986000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21165322%2F00143.00_02_13_25.Still004.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwatch-delhi-floofs-g20-eviction-homeless%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20problems%20of%20the%20already%20homeless%20people%20of%20Delhi's%20Bela%20estate%20have%20doubled%20after%20the%20recent%20flooding%20of%20the%20Yamuna%20in%20the%20national%20capital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Furban%2Fwatch-delhi-floofs-g20-eviction-homeless%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Studies%20On%20For%20Sudden%20Cardiac%20Arrest%20Cases%20Among%20Young%20After%20Covid%3A%20Centre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESudden%20deaths%20due%20to%20cardiac%20arrest%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20young%20people%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20but%20sufficient%20evidence%20is%20not%20available%20to%20confirm%20the%20cause%2C%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20told%20Parliament%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Council%20of%20Medical%20Research%20is%20conducting%20three%20different%20studies%20to%20ascertain%20the%20facts%20regarding%20rising%20cases%20of%20cardiac%20arrest%20after%20the%20pandemic%2C%20Mr%20Mandaviya%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20question%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20a%20multi-centric%20matched%20case%20control%20study%20on%20factors%20associated%20with%20sudden%20deaths%20among%20adults%20aged%2018%20to%2045%20in%20India%20is%20ongoing%20at%20around%2040%20hospitals%2Fresearch%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20multicentric%20hospital-based%20matched%20case%20control%20study%20is%20underway%20at%20around%2030%20COVID-19%20clinical%20registry%20hospitals%20to%20determine%20the%20effect%20of%20the%20Covid%20vaccine%20on%20thrombotic%20events%20among%20the%20population%20aged%2018%20to%2045%20in%202022%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20another%20study%20for%20establishing%20the%20cause%20of%20sudden%20unexplained%20deaths%20in%20young%20people%20through%20virtual%20and%20physical%20autopsy%20is%20underway%2C%20Mandaviya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20health%20issues%20related%20to%20cardiovascular%20disease%2C%20the%20Centre's%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Family%20Welfare%20provides%20technical%20and%20financial%20support%20to%20states%20and%20Union%20Territories%20under%20the%20National%20Programme%20for%20Prevention%20and%20Control%20of%20Non-Communicable%20Diseases%20(NP-NCD).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECardiovascular%20disease%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20NP-NCD.%20The%20programme%20includes%20strengthening%20infrastructure%2C%20human%20resource%20development%2C%20health%20promotion%2C%20population-based%20screening%20of%20the%20population%20in%20the%2030-year%20and%20above%20age%20group%20under%20the%20Ayushman%20Bharat%20Health%20Wellness%20Centre%2C%20early%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20management%20and%20referral%20to%20an%20appropriate%20level%20of%20health%20care%20facility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20NP-NCD%2C%20724%20district%20non-communicable%20disease%20clinics%2C%20210%20district%20cardiac%20care%20units%2C%20326%20district%20day%20care%20centres%20and%206%2C110%20community%20health%20centre%20non-communicable%20disease%20clinics%20have%20been%20set%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECardiovascular%20disease%20patients%20are%20getting%20treatment%20at%20various%20health%20facilities%20in%20the%20healthcare%20delivery%20system%2C%20including%20medical%20colleges%2C%20central%20institutes%20such%20as%20AIIMS%2C%20central%20government%20and%20private%20sector%20hospitals%2C%20Mandaviya%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20focus%20on%20cardiovascular%20diseases%20in%20its%20various%20aspects%20in%20case%20of%20new%20AIIMS%20and%20many%20upgraded%20institutions%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Swasthya%20Suraksha%20Yojana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20facilitate%20accessible%20and%20affordable%20health%20care%20and%20treatment%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Jan%20Arogya%20Yojana%20(PMJAY)%2C%20health%20insurance%20cover%20of%20Rs%205%20lakh%20per%20family%20per%20year%20for%20secondary%20or%20tertiary%20care%20hospitalisation%20is%20provided%20to%20over%2060%20crore%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20treatment%20packages%20are%20comprehensive%2C%20covering%20various%20treatment%20related%20aspects%20such%20as%20drugs%20and%20diagnostic%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20umbrella%20scheme%20of%20the%20Rashtriya%20Arogya%20Nidhi%2C%20financial%20assistance%20is%20provided%20to%20families%20living%20below%20the%20threshold%20poverty%20line%20for%20treatment%20in%20government%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20quality%20generic%20medicines%20are%20made%20available%20at%20affordable%20prices%20to%20all%20under%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Bhartiya%20Janaushadhi%20Pariyojana%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAffordable%20medicines%20and%20reliable%20implants%20for%20treatment%20(AMRIT)%20pharmacy%20stores%20have%20been%20set%20up%20in%20some%20hospitals%2Finstitutions%20with%20an%20objective%20to%20make%20available%20cardiovascular%20drugs%20at%20a%20substantial%20discount%2C%20vis-a-vis%20the%20maximum%20retail%20price.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689938580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Fqrkq57t_coronavirus-india-generic-hospital-generic-covid-hospital-reuters-650_625x300_10_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fstudies-on-for-sudden-cardiac-arrest-cases-among-young-after-covid-centre-4228953%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sudden%20deaths%20due%20to%20cardiac%20arrest%20have%20been%20reported%20in%20young%20people%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20but%20sufficient%20evidence%20is%20not%20available%20to%20confirm%20the%20cause%2C%20Union%20Health%20Minister%20Mansukh%20Mandaviya%20told%20Parliament%20today.%22%2C%22author%