0El%20Paso%20to%20Silver%20City%2C%20Gallup%2C%20Sorocco%20and%20Albuquerque%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3D2699e23e96c8d1d92c8f56a4a2cf21b4db9d164652fe5c0197de817f606bbbca%26postID%3D64ba42842db2814246fbb996%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.newspapers.com%252Farticle%252F3985966%252F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20an%20August%2031%2C%201945%2C%20report%20in%20the%20El%20Paso%20Herald-Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20responsibility%20for%20drafting%20a%20series%20of%20press%20releases%20explaining%20this%20away%20fell%20to%20a%20New%20York%20Times%20science%20reporter%2C%20William%20Laurence%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.history.army.mil%2Fhtml%2Fbooks%2F011%2F11-10%2FCMH_Pub_11-10.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Vincent%20C.%20Jones%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20chronicled%20the%20test%20for%20the%20US%20Army%20Center%20of%20Military%20History.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELaurence%20was%20temporarily%20released%20from%20his%20job%20at%20the%20Times%20to%20help%20the%20Manhattan%20Project%2C%20Jones%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20total%2C%20Laurence%20helped%20draft%20four%20press%20releases%20%E2%80%94%20the%20other%20three%20covered%20potentially%20catastrophic%20results%20such%20as%20having%20to%20evacuate%20residents%2C%20damage%20to%20towns%2C%20and%20draft%20death%20notices%2C%20per%20Jones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnly%20the%20one%20below%20was%20ever%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20August%2031%20article%2C%20more%20than%20a%20month%20later%2C%20the%20Herald-Post%20reported%20that%20the%20blast%20was%20actually%20the%20%26quot%3BA-bomb%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0%20admitting%20it%20had%20been%20duped%20by%20the%20earlier%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wrote%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20was%20the%20story%20of%20the%20half-century%2C%20and%20newsmen%20didn't%20know%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20New%20Mexico's%20Clovis%20News-Journal%20article%20from%20July%2016%2C%201945%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EBlast%20occurs%20at%20Alamogordo%20Army%20Air%20Base%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EALAMOGORDO%2C%20N.M.%2C%20July%2016.%20N%20---%20William%20O.%20Eareckson%2C%20commanding%20officer%20of%20the%20Alamogordo%20army%20air%20base%20made%20the%20following%20statement%20today%3A%20%26quot%3BSeveral%20inquiries%20have%20been%20received%20concerning%20a%20heavy%20explosion%20which%20occurred%20on%20the%20Alamogordo%20Air%20Base%20this%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20remotely%20located%20ammunition%20magazine%20containing%20a%20considerable%20amount%20of%20high%20explosive%20and%20pyrotechnics%20exploded.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20loss%20of%20life%20or%20injury%20to%20anyone%2C%20and%20property%20damage%20outside%20of%20the%20explosives%20magazine%20itself%20was%20negligible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWeather%20conditions%20affecting%20the%20content%20of%20gas%20shells%20exploded%20by%20the%20balst%20%5Bsic%5D%20may%20make%20it%20desirable%20for%20the%20army%20to%20evacuate%20temporarily%20a%20few%20civilians%20from%20their%20homes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foppenheimer-explanation-local-news-trinity-nuclear-bomb-test-cover-up-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689938067000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64ba534303c40c001a977149%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foppenheimer-explanation-local-news-trinity-nuclear-bomb-test-cover-up-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20bogus%20explanation%20for%20the%20blast%20that%20was%20actually%20Oppeneimer's%20first%20nuclear%20bomb%20test%20was%20buried%20in%20tiny%20news%20releases%20designed%20to%20hush%20it%20up.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Mia%20Jankowicz)%22%2C%22engagement%