20in%20the%20grandest%20possible%20way%2C%20the%20story%20of%20J.%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%2C%20the%20father%20of%20the%20atomic%20bomb%20who%20lived%20to%20see%20the%20devastation%20and%20long-term%20dangers%20that%20his%20weapon%20of%20mass%20destruction%20unleashed%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20cinematic%20achievement%20of%20blinding%20brilliance%2C%20achieves%20a%20sublime%20combination%20of%20visual%20grandeur%2C%20technical%20flair%2C%20emotional%20intimacy%20and%20an%20examination%20of%20the%20limits%20of%20human%20endeavour%20and%20ambition.%20Through%20all%20the%20layers%20that%20constitute%20the%20film%2C%20what%20peeps%20out%20most%20prominently%20is%20the%20director's%20unambiguous%20acknowledgement%20of%20the%20ethical%20questions%20that%20surround%20the%20brilliant%20American%20theoretical%20physicist's%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20more%20superficial%20level%2C%20the%20film%20gives%20the%20writer-director%20the%20scope%20to%20orchestrate%20the%20elements%20of%20space%20and%20time%20in%20a%20straightforward%20but%20a%20highly%20enthralling%20manner%20and%20tap%20the%20dramatic%20potential%20of%20the%20tragic%20story%20of%20a%20genius%20who%20pushed%20the%20boundaries%20of%20quantum%20physics%20only%20to%20trigger%20a%20dangerous%20arms%20race.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20three-hour%20epic%20is%20about%20a%20man%2C%20quantum%20physics%2C%20and%20a%20point%20in%20history%2C%20but%20it%20comes%20off%20as%20a%20timeless%2C%20almost%20Shakespearean%20morality%20tale%20about%20an%20impossible%20achievement%20and%20its%20horrific%20consequences.%20The%20film%20crammed%20with%20diverse%20narrative%20and%20spatial%20elements%20that%20Nolan%20and%20his%20cinematographer%20Hoyte%20van%20Hoytema%20harness%20and%20press%20into%20the%20service%20of%20an%20engrossing%20story%20about%20science%2C%20war%20and%20political%20vendetta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20isn't%2C%20however%2C%20only%20the%20formal%20attributes%20of%20the%20film%20that%20are%20impressive.%20Its%20thematic%20depth%20turns%20it%20into%20an%20introspection%20(no%20matter%20how%20wordy)%20on%20science%2C%20weapons%20and%20the%20horrors%20of%20war%20without%20actually%20putting%20footage%20of%20the%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20bombings%20and%20their%20effects%20on%20the%20screen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20scientist%20who%20unwittingly%20armed%20the%20human%20race%20with%20a%20self-destruct%20button%2C%20Oppenheimer%2C%20played%20with%20unwavering%20solidity%20by%20regular%20Nolan%20collaborator%20Cillian%20Murphy%2C%20is%20presented%20as%20a%20genius%20who%20pays%20as%20high%20a%20price%20for%20his%20deadly%20invention%20as%20he%20does%20for%20his%20subsequent%20decision%20to%20turn%20into%20an%20advocate%20for%20nuclear%20arms%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20excitement%20of%20scientific%20research%2C%20the%20upshots%20by%20political%20exigencies%20and%20the%20workings%20of%20personal%20relationships%20are%20all%20woven%20into%20the%20dense%20but%20never%20less%20than%20dynamic%20storyline.%20Nolan%2C%20with%20the%20aid%20of%20Murphy%2C%20turns%20Oppenheimer%20into%20a%20figure%20who%20inspires%20awe%20and%20admiration%20to%20begin%20with.%20But%20as%20a%20powerful%20adversary%20turns%20against%20him%20and%20seeks%20to%20corner%20him%20by%20harping%20on%20his%20pro-left%20affiliations%2C%20the%20hero%20turns%20into%20a%20hapless%20victim%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bkangaroo%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOppenheimer's%20wife%20Kitty%20(a%20terrific%20Emily%20Blunt)%20and%20the%20firebrand%20Communist%20Jean%20Tatlock%20(Florence%20Pugh%20in%20a%20memorable%20cameo)%20with%20whom%20he%20has%20an%20affair%20are%20integral%20parts%20of%20the%20story%2C%20as%20are%20the%20friends%20and%20rivals%20who%20surround%20the%20scientist%20as%20he%20works%20on%20the%20bomb%20in%20the%20hope%20that%20it%20would%20end%20all%20wars.%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20atomic%20bomb%20that%20Oppenheimer%20delivers%20to%20the%20US%20military%20does%20bring%20World%20War%20II%20to%20an%20end%20in%20the%20Pacific%2C%20but%20it%20also%20starts%20a%20public%20battle%20that%20a%20national%20hero%20has%20to%20fight%20to%20protect%20his%20own%20reputation%20as%20well%20as%20a%20moral%20conflict%20that%20is%20triggered%20by%20pangs%20of%20guilt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FuYPbbksJxIg%3Fsi%3Dxdo9SwdWSzMlMVuQ%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20come%20close%20to%20being%20weighed%20down%20by%20an%20information%20overload%2C%20but%20in%20Nolan's%20hand%20every%20little%20piece%20that%20goes%20into%20the%20narrative%20and%20every%20single%20actor%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20length%20of%20the%20role%20or%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20presence%2C%20has%20considerable%20weight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20film%20alternates%20between%20luminous%20colour%20and%20vivid%20black-and-white%20as%20it%20straddles%20several%20decades%20in%20the%20life%20of%20the%20protagonist%20-%20from%20his%20days%20as%20a%20student%20in%20the%201920%20to%20his%20years%20as%20a%20greying%20man%20struggling%20till%20the%20end%20of%20his%20life%20to%20live%20down%20his%20controversial%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENolan's%20screenplay%20splits%20the%20story%20into%20three%20broad%20segments.%20The%20centrepiece%20is%20the%20complex%20and%20arduous%20process%20of%20the%20building%20of%20the%20bomb%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Manhattan%20Project%20at%20a%20clandestine%20laboratory%20in%20Los%20Alamos%2C%20New%20Mexico%2C%20headed%20by%20Oppenheimer%2C%20manned%20by%20some%20of%20the%20most%20exceptional%20scientists%20of%20the%20era%20and%20operated%20under%20the%20military%20supervision%20of%20the%20curt%20General%20Leslie%20Groves%20(Matt%20Damon).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIntercut%20into%20the%20mid-1940s%20core%20section%20of%20the%20story%20are%20a%201959%20confirmation%20hearing%20(filmed%20in%20black%20and%20white)%20for%20the%20elevation%20to%20the%20cabinet%20of%20the%20former%20chairman%20of%20the%20US%20Atomic%20Energy%20Commission%2C%20Admiral%20Lewis%20Strauss%20(a%20barely%20recognisable%20Robert%20Downey%20Jr.)%20and%20a%201954%20security%20clearance%20inquiry%20against%20Oppenheimer.%20Both%20enhance%20the%20kinetic%20energy%20that%20courses%20through%20the%20tale.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rhythm%20of%20Jennifer%20Lame's%20editing%20imparts%20sustained%20momentum%20to%20the%20film%20as%20it%20cuts%20back%20and%20forth%20between%20the%20three%20blocks.%20The%20pace%20never%20flags.%20The%20film%20plays%20out%20like%20a%20cross%20between%20a%20richly%20textured%20saga%20of%20an%20epochal%20scientific%20achievement%20and%20an%20inquisition%20into%20decisions%20and%20acts%20that%20have%20had%20a%20far-reaching%20impact%20on%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20%3Cem%3EAmerican%20Prometheus%3A%20The%20Triumph%20and%20Tragedy%20of%20J.%20Robert%20Oppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20tell-all%202005%20biography%20by%20Kai%20Bird%20and%20Martin%20J.%20Sherwin%2C%20the%20film%20borrows%20freely%20from%20the%20book%20and%20crafts%20a%20cinematic%20work%20that%20sucks%20you%20in%20instantly%20and%20throws%20up%20ideas%20that%20demand%20absolute%20attention.%20It%20is%20a%20complete%20cinematic%20experience%20that%20equal%20parts%20thought-provoking%20and%20thrilling.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20a%20staggeringly%20good%20job%20of%20transporting%20the%20audience%20to%20another%20era%2C%20but%20it%20speaks%20to%20our%20time%20in%20a%20way%20that%20is%20palpable%20and%20relevant.%20It%20is%20the%20sort%20of%20film%20that%20is%20as%20a%20much%20a%20story%20of%20an%20individual%20and%20his%20contentious%20achievement%20as%20of%20an%20entire%20century%20caught%20in%20an%20endless%20cycle%20of%20war%20and%20human%20suffering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3Cem%3EOppenheimer%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20as%20important%20a%20film%20as%20any%20that%20Nolan%20has%20ever%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689937560000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fie9svi98_cillian_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foppenheimer-review-a-cinematic-achievement-of-blinding-brilliance-4-5-stars-4229264%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Oppenheimer%20Review%3A%20Oppenheimer%2C%20played%20with%20unwavering%20solidity%20by%20Cillian%20Murphy%2C%20is%20presented%20as%20a%20genius%20who%20pays%20as%20high%20a%20price%20for%20his%20deadly%20invention%20as%20for%20his%20subsequent%20decision%20to%20turn%20into%20an%20advocate%20for%20nuclear%20arms%20control.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foppenheimer-review-a-cinematic-achievement-of-blinding-brilliance-4-5-stars-4229264%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foppenheimer-review-a-cinematic-achievement-of-blinding-brilliance-4-5-stars-4229264%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Foppenheimer-review-a-cinematic-achievement-of-blinding-brilliance-4-5-stars-4229264%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DU%20Student%20Detained%20Without%20Orders%20Ahead%20of%20PM%20Event%20Files%20Police%20Complaint%20After%20HC%20Green%20Light%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30141622%2FUntitled-design-14.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%20Delhi%20University%20student%20activist%20Abhigyan%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-camps-inside-du-student-activists-house-bars-them-from-leaving-during-pm-event%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%93%20who%20was%20confined%20to%20his%20house%20by%20Model%20Town%20constables%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20June%2030%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20visit%20to%20campus%20%E2%80%93%20has%20filed%20a%20formal%20complaint%20of%20wrongful%20confinement%20with%20his%20local%20police%20station%20after%20the%20Delhi%20high%20court%20said%20he%20had%20the%20right%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20green%20light%20came%20after%20counsel%20for%20the%20Delhi%20police%2C%20Sanjay%20Lao%2C%20told%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20of%20the%20court%20that%20there%20were%20no%20preventive%20detention%20orders%20against%20Abhighyan.%20The%20cour%3Cspan%3Et%20was%20hearing%20a%20writ%20petition%20by%20Abhigyan%20alleging%20that%20his%20preventive%20detention%20was%20illegal%20as%20it%20was%20without%20orders.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbhigyan%20had%20also%20petitioned%20the%20court%20to%20declare%20his%20confinement%20as%20illegal%20and%20issue%20a%20writ%20of%20mandamus%20censuring%20the%20practice%20of%20arbitrary%20detention.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20bench%20comprising%20Justices%20Siddharth%20Mridul%20and%20Gaurang%20Kanth%20said%20it%20would%20be%20premature%20for%20the%20court%20to%20issue%20such%20a%20declaration%2C%20it%20granted%20him%20liberty%20on%20July%2012%20to%20file%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20Model%20Town%20police%E2%80%99s%20station%20house%20officer%20(SHO).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20July%2017%2C%20Abhigyan%20filed%20his%20complaint%20against%20constables%20Kaberi%20and%20Amit%20Kumar%20citing%20several%20sections%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code.%20The%20complaint%20was%20duly%20received%20and%20the%20police%20will%20now%20have%20to%20conduct%20a%20preliminary%20investigation%20before%20registering%20%E2%80%93%20or%20refusing%20to%20register%20%E2%80%93%20an%20FIR.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIllegal%20custody%20is%20an%20anathema%20and%20antithesis%20of%20rule%20of%20law%2C%20but%20the%20law%20applies%20equally%20to%20the%20police%20as%20it%20does%20to%20you%20%E2%80%A6%20Your%20allegation%20is%20for%20illegal%20detention.%20You%20file%20a%20complaint.%20The%20police%20%5Bdo%5D%20not%20have%20any%20immunity%20for%20their%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Mridul%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fhigh-court%2Fdelhi-high-court%2Fdelhi-high-court-complaint-delhi-police-aisa-activist-illegal-detention-prime-minister-visit-du-232540%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eremarked%20orally%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20according%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20also%20likened%20the%20idea%20of%20the%20court%20making%20such%20a%20declaration%20at%20that%20stage%20in%20the%20case%20to%20%E2%80%9Cputting%20the%20cart%20before%20the%20horse%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbhigyan%20is%20a%20student%20at%20Delhi%20University%20(DU)%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Delhi%20chapter%20of%20the%20All%20India%20Students%E2%80%99%20Association%20(AISA)%2C%20a%20student%20body%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fweb.archive.org%2Fweb%2F20230701023648%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fwww.aisa.in%2Fabout%2Fmanifesto%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eassociated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20with%20the%20Communist%20Party%20of%20India%20(Marxist-Leninist)%20Liberation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20was%20confined%20by%20police%20along%20with%20fellow%20DU%20student%20and%20AISA%20general%20secretary%20Anjali%20in%20the%20latter%E2%80%99s%20home%20on%20June%2030%2C%20hours%20ahead%20of%20a%20ceremony%20in%20the%20university%E2%80%99s%20centenary%20celebrations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30142414%2FIMG-20230630-WA0009-1-1024x576.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30142414%2FIMG-20230630-WA0009-1-1024x576.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30142414%2FIMG-20230630-WA0009-1-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F06%2F30142414%2FIMG-20230630-WA0009-1.jpg%201200w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-660936%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22473%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EConstables%20from%20the%20Model%20Town%20police%20station%20inside%20the%20student%20activist%E2%80%99s%20home.%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20was%20booked%20as%20the%20ceremony%E2%80%99s%20chief%20guest.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20university%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fdu-colleges-stir-controversy-with-mandatory-attendance-for-valedictory-ceremony%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewent%20out%20of%20its%20way%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20to%20ensure%20student%20compliance%20during%20the%20ceremony%2C%20with%20some%20of%20its%20colleges%20mandating%20attendance%20at%20screenings%20of%20the%20event%20and%20barring%20students%20from%20wearing%20black-coloured%20clothing%2C%20a%20common%20symbol%20of%20dissent.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModel%20Town%20police%20allegedly%20told%20Abhigyan%20and%20Anjali%20that%20they%20were%20being%20detained%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%9D%20as%20they%20%E2%80%9Cmight%20create%20%5Ba%5D%20ruckus%20at%20the%20DU%20event%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EConstables%20Kaberi%20and%20Amit%20Kumar%20camped%20in%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20home%20for%20five%20hours%20on%20June%2030%20starting%20at%20around%209%20am%20and%20allegedly%20threatened%20to%20arrest%20the%20AISA%20activists%20if%20they%20tried%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20also%20allegedly%20told%20Abhigyan%20that%20there%20were%20no%20orders%20for%20his%20and%20Anjali%E2%80%99s%20detention%2C%20something%20that%20has%20since%20been%20corroborated%20by%20standing%20counsel%20Lao%20in%20court.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdvocate%20Shahrukh%20Alam%2C%20who%20represented%20Abhigyan%20in%20the%20high%20court%2C%20said%20that%20their%20case%20centred%20on%20the%20circumstances%20under%20which%20someone%E2%80%99s%20fundamental%20rights%20to%20personal%20liberty%20(Article%2021%20of%20the%20constitution)%20and%20protection%20from%20arbitrary%20detention%20(Article%2022)%20may%20be%20breached.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20questions%20for%20consideration%20are%3A%20(1)%20If%20the%20breach%20of%20liberty%20is%20only%20for%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20is%20it%20acceptable%20to%20suspend%20%5Bsomeone%E2%80%99s%5D%20Article%2021%20and%20Article%2022%20rights%3F%20(2)%20If%20the%20breach%20of%20liberty%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Evis-a-vis%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20known%20protestors%2C%20raucous%20student%20activists%20and%20dissenters%2C%20is%20it%20acceptable%20to%20suspend%20%5Btheir%5D%20Article%2021%20and%20Article%2022%20rights%3F%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlam%20said%20the%20answer%20to%20these%20questions%20is%20to%20be%20found%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EK.S.%20Puttaswamy%20v.%20Union%20of%20India%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20in%20which%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20said%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EADM%20Jabalpur%20v.%20Shivkant%20Shukla%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20a%20judgement%20which%20had%20endorsed%20the%20suspension%20of%20fundamental%20rights%20during%20emergency%2C%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fopinion%2Fcolumns%2Fthe-verdict-of-history-adm-jabalpur-case-5942547%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eburied%20ten%20fathoms%20deep%20and%20is%20never%20to%20be%20resurrected%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThus%2C%20the%20primacy%20of%20fundamental%20rights%20is%20well%20established%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20argued.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20Read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fjustice-chandrachud-judgment-right-to-privacy%5C%22%3EKey%20Highlights%20of%20Justice%20Chandrachud%E2%80%99s%20Judgment%20in%20the%20Right%20to%20Privacy%20Case%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbhigyan%E2%80%99s%20lawyers%20also%20noted%20in%20their%20writ%20petition%20dated%20July%2010%20that%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20held%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findiankanoon.org%2Fdoc%2F564452%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Edifferent%20case%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20under%20Article%2022%20(5)%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20authorities%20who%20order%20the%20preventive%20detention%20of%20a%20person%20must%20communicate%20the%20grounds%20of%20the%20order%20to%20that%20person%20as%20soon%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThey%20argued%20that%20as%20Abhigyan%20was%20never%20provided%20with%20an%20order%20(or%20grounds%20for%20an%20order)%20relating%20to%20his%20detention%2C%20his%20fundamental%20right%20under%20Article%2022%20had%20been%20violated.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAlam%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20that%20the%20high%20court%E2%80%99s%20July%2012%20order%20granting%20liberty%20to%20Abhigyan%20was%20especially%20significant%20because%20of%20a%20letter%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20registrar%20general%20sent%20to%20the%20Model%20Town%20SHO%20asking%20for%20their%20immediate%20compliance%20with%20the%20order.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20significant%20for%20the%20cover%20letter%20from%20the%20registrar%20general%20to%20the%20SHO%20of%20the%20Model%20Town%20police%20station%20directing%20immediate%20compliance%20with%20the%20order.%20It%20is%20interesting%20because%20normally%2C%20orders%20aren%E2%80%99t%20directly%20communicated%20to%20police%20stations%2C%20unless%20it%20is%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20case.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20habeas%20corpus%20cases%2C%20when%20someone%20is%20under%20illegal%20detention%2C%20orders%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20person%E2%80%99s%20custodian.%20But%20Abhigyan%E2%80%99s%20is%20not%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20case%20%E2%80%93%20it%20is%20a%20preventive%20detention%20case%2C%20and%20the%20court%E2%80%99s%20order%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Epost%20facto%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20%5Bafter%20the%20fact%5D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20court%E2%80%99s%20action%20recognises%20that%20Abhigyan%E2%80%99s%20detention%20was%20illegal%20as%20there%20were%20no%20orders%20for%20it%2C%20and%20that%20cases%20like%20these%20are%20becoming%20a%20pattern%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21135811%2FAnjali-and-Abhigyan-1024x768.jpeg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22627%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21135811%2FAnjali-and-Abhigyan-1024x768.jpeg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21135811%2FAnjali-and-Abhigyan-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21135811%2FAnjali-and-Abhigyan.jpeg%201080w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664362%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22470%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAnjali%20and%20Abhigyan%20under%20detention%20in%20the%20former%E2%80%99s%20flat%20on%20June%2030.%20Photo%3A%20Twitter%2F%40anjali__27.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20of%20July%2019%2C%20Advocate%20Archit%20Krishna%2C%20who%20also%20represented%20Abhigyan%20in%20court%2C%20said%20that%20no%20FIR%20had%20been%20filed.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20added%20that%20if%20no%20FIR%20is%20filed%20eventually%2C%20Abhigyan%20has%20the%20legal%20recourse%20to%20approach%20a%20magistrate%20under%20sections%20156%20(3)%20and%20200%20of%20the%20Code%20of%20Criminal%20Procedure%20seeking%20the%20court%20to%20order%20the%20police%20to%20file%20an%20FIR.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20his%20request%20to%20the%20SHO%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20has%20accessed%2C%20Abhigyan%20said%20that%20his%20confinement%20by%20the%20constables%20has%20damaged%20his%20standing%20in%20the%20community.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20whole%20incident%20%E2%80%A6%20resulted%20in%20the%20neighbours%20complaining%20and%20demanding%20explanations%20from%20me%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20and%20declaring%20that%20their%20presence%20in%20the%20apartment%20was%20not%20welcome.%20My%20friends%20and%20I%20have%20had%20to%20face%20a%20lot%20of%20hostility%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20have%20been%20subjected%20to%20general%20suspicion%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnjali%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fdelhi-police-camps-inside-du-student-activists-house-bars-them-from-leaving-during-pm-event%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epreviously%20told%20%3C%2Fspan%