%2C%2035-year-old%20Joseph%2C%20and%2029-year-old%20Jordan%20were%20convicted%20by%20a%20federal%20jury%20in%20Miami%20on%20charges%20of%20conspiring%20to%20defraud%20the%20United%20States%20and%20delivering%20misbranded%20drugs%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.miamiherald.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2Farticle277475553.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Miami%20Herald%20reported.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fusao-sdfl%2Fpr%2Fleader-genesis-ii-church-health-and-healing-who-sold-toxic-bleach-fake-miracle-cure%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EProsecutors%20said%20the%20family%20%3C%2Fa%3Esold%20%26quot%3BMiracle%20Mineral%20Solution%26quot%3B%20through%20their%20Genesis%20II%20church.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20online%20videos%2C%20seminars%2C%20and%20on%20their%20website%2C%20the%20Grenons%20advocated%20drinking%20sodium%20chlorite%20diluted%20with%20a%20household%20acid%2C%20such%20as%20lemon%20juice%2C%20thus%20creating%20chlorine%20dioxide%2C%20a%20powerful%20industrial%20bleach%20used%20to%20treat%20wood%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20substance%20is%20highly%20dangerous%20to%20consume%2C%20and%20can%20cause%20severe%20vomiting%2C%20severe%20diarrhea%2C%20life-threatening%20low%20blood%20pressure%20caused%20by%20dehydration%2C%20and%20acute%20liver%20failure%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fda.gov%2Fconsumers%2Fconsumer-updates%2Fdanger-dont-drink-miracle-mineral-solution-or-similar-products%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esays%20the%20US%20Food%20and%20Drugs%20Administration.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmms-bleach-killed-7-americans-new-from-colombia-arrest-2020-8%3Fr%3DUS%26IR%3DT%5C%22%3EUS%20officials%20in%20legal%20documents%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20the%20bleach%20had%20been%20linked%20to%20seven%20deaths%20in%20the%20US.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E