mands%20Entire%20Speech%20Be%20Put%20On%20Record%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETrinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20demanding%20that%20his%20entire%20speech%20on%20July%2020%20in%20the%20House%20be%20put%20on%20record%20as%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Brightfully%26quot%3B%20questioned%20the%20government%20on%20the%20alarming%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EParts%20of%20the%20MP's%20speech%20in%20the%20House%20were%20expunged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPhrases%20from%20my%20point%20of%20order%20on%2020%20July%202023%20were%20expunged%20by%20the%20exercise%20of%20the%20Presiding%20Officer's%20discretion.%20The%20Point%20of%20Order%20made%20by%20me%20on%20July%2020%2C%202023%2C%20was%20an%20attempt%20as%20leader%20of%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20opposition%20parties%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20to%20duly%20and%20rightfully%20question%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20and%20the%20Government%20in%20power%20about%20the%20alarming%20and%20distressful%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20O'Brien%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Point%20of%20Order%20made%20by%20me%20and%20the%20questions%20asked%20therein%20were%20within%20the%20true%20essence%20of%20democracy%20and%20anything%20but%20'Unparliamentary'.%20I%20had%20simply%20asked%20for%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20speak%20up%20on%20Manipur%20in%20Parliament%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDerek%20O'Brien%20said%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Secretariat%20issued%20a%20booklet%20listing%20down%20words%20and%20expressions%20that%20were%20to%20be%20regarded%20as%20%26quot%3Bunparliamentary%26quot%3B%20including%20commonly%20used%20words%20such%20as%20ashamed%2C%20abused%2C%20betrayed%2C%20corrupt%2C%20drama%2C%20hypocrisy%2C%20and%20incompetent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20close%20perusal%20of%20the%20above%20mentioned%20makes%20it%20apparent%20that%20recent%20additions%20to%20this%20list%20are%20replete%20with%20words%20that%20have%20been%20explicitly%20used%20in%20recent%20years%20by%20the%20Opposition%20to%20describe%20the%20Union%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20TMC%20MP%20alleged%20that%20the%20act%20of%20declaring%20words%20used%20to%20criticise%20the%20government%20in%20power%20as%20%26quot%3Banti-union%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bunparliamentary%26quot%3B%20is%20a%20blatant%20attempt%20at%20muzzling%20the%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20problem%20is%20not%20that%20the%20Constitution%20does%20not%20guarantee%20free%20speech%2C%20but%20that%20it%20is%20easy%20to%20silence%20free%20speech%20because%20of%20a%20combination%20of%20overbroad%20laws%20like%20this%20one.%20In%20light%20of%20the%20above%20and%20in%20light%20of%20the%20power%20bestowed%20upon%20the%20Hon'ble%20Chairman%2C%20I%20demand%20that%20my%20full%20speech%20be%20put%20on%20record%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20O'Brien%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20has%20been%20a%20bone%20of%20contention%20between%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20government%20since%20Parliament's%20Monsoon%20session%20began%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689934620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fd31tspng_derek-obrien-pti_625x300_21_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmanipur-references-expunged-trinamool-mp-derek-obrien-demands-full-rajya-sabha-speech-be-put-on-record-4229063%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Trinamool%20Congress%20MP%20Derek%20O'Brien%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Chairman%20demanding%20that%20his%20entire%20speech%20on%20July%2020%20in%20the%20House%20be%20put%20on%20record%20as%20he%20had%20%26quot%3Brightfully%26quot%3B%20questioned%20the%20government%2