e%20outlet%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20referring%20to%20his%20film%20'%3Cem%3EThe%20Terminator%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20which%20revolves%20around%20a%20cybernetic%20assassin%20created%20by%20an%20intelligent%20supercomputer%20known%20as%20Skynet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Mr%20Cameron%2C%20the%20biggest%20danger%20lies%20in%20the%20weaponisation%20of%20the%20new%20technology.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20we%20will%20get%20into%20the%20equivalent%20of%20a%20nuclear%20arms%20race%20with%20AI.%20And%20if%20we%20don't%20build%20it%2C%20the%20other%20guys%20are%20for%20sure%20going%20to%20build%20it%2C%20and%20so%20then%20it'll%20escalate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Mr%20Cameron's%20vision%20of%20AI%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%20computers%20might%20operate%20so%20rapidly%20that%20humans%20would%20be%20unable%20to%20intervene%2C%20eliminating%20the%20possibility%20of%20peace%20talks%20or%20armistice.%20Dealing%20with%20such%20technology%20requires%20a%20focus%20on%20de-escalation%2C%20but%20the%20director%20said%20he%20doubts%20that%20AI%20systems%20would%20adhere%20to%20such%20principles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Cameron%20has%20previously%20expressed%20similar%20concerns%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20while%20AI%20has%20its%20advantages%2C%20it%20could%20also%20lead%20to%20disastrous%20consequences%20and%20potentially%20spell%20the%20end%20of%20the%20world.%20He%20has%20even%20speculated%20that%20sentient%20computers%20might%20already%20be%20manipulating%20the%20world%20%26quot%3Bwithout%20our%20knowledge%2C%20with%20total%20control%20over%20all%20media%20and%20information%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeading%20experts%20in%20the%20field%20have%20also%20echoed%20these%20warnings.%20Tech%20giants%20like%20OpenAI%20and%20Google's%20DeepMind%2C%20along%20with%20academics%2C%20lawmakers%2C%20and%20entrepreneurs%2C%20have%20called%20for%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20the%20risks%20associated%20with%20AI.%20They%20stress%20that%20addressing%20these%20concerns%20should%20be%20a%20global%20priority%20on%20par%20with%20addressing%20pandemics%20and%20nuclear%20war%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20open%20letter%20signed%20by%20over%201%2C000%20experts%20and%20executives%2C%20including%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20Steve%20Wozniak%2C%20has%20urged%20for%20a%20six-month%20pause%20on%20training%20powerful%20AI%20systems%20until%20their%20positive%20effects%20can%20be%20assured%20and%20risks%20managed.%20These%20concerns%20stem%20from%20the%20belief%20that%20AI%20could%20pose%20profound%20risks%20to%20society%20and%20humanity%20at%20large.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689934140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F1h56904g_james-cameron_625x300_13_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-warned-you-guys-in-1984-terminator-director-james-cameron-on-ai-4229027%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22James%20Cameron%20has%20previously%20expressed%20similar%20concerns%2C%20acknowledging%20that%20while%20AI%20has%20its%20advantages%2C%20it%20could%20also%20lead%20to%20disastrous%20consequences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-warned-you-guys-in-1984-terminator-director-james-cameron-on-ai-4229027%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-warned-you-guys-in-1984-terminator-director-james-cameron-on-ai-4229027%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fi-warned-you-guys-in-1984-terminator-director-james-cameron-on-ai-4229027%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ambassador%20criticised%20'sarcastic'%20Zelenskyy%20in%20Sky%20News%20interview%20days%20before%20sacking%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689934140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-vadym-prystaiko-ukrainian_6225461.jpg%3F20230721101952%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2F