%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Association%20also%20highlighted%20the%20remarks%20made%20by%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20(CJI)%20D.Y.%20Chandrachud%20on%20the%20sexual%20violence%20during%20the%20riot%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20women%20as%20instruments%20of%20perpetrating%20violence%20in%20a%20charged%20atmosphere%20is%20simply%20unacceptable%20in%20a%20constitutional%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20three-judge%20bench%20headed%20by%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fmanipur-sexual-assault-using-women-as-instruments-of-violence-is-unacceptable-says-cji%2Farticle67100560.ece%5C%22%3Esaid.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Justice%20also%20gave%20an%20ultimatum%20to%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20the%20Manipur%20government%20to%20either%20book%20the%20perpetrators%2C%20or%20step%20aside%20for%20the%20judiciary%20to%20step%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20addressing%20Attorney%20General%20R.%20Venkataramani%20and%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeparately%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20Bar%20Association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-bar-association-manipur-sexual-assault-video-condemns-inaction-state-police-arresting-culprits-233310%5C%22%3Ehas%20also%20passed%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20resolution%2C%20condemning%20the%20May%204%20incident%2C%20and%20saying%20that%20the%20gender-based%20violence%20and%20humiliation%20has%20far-reaching%20consequences%20on%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20physical%20and%20psychological%20well-being%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20condemned%20the%20inaction%20of%20the%20state%20police%20in%20holding%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSuch%20incidents%20in%20Manipur%20which%20have%20been%20taking%20place%20since%20have%20not%20only%20brought%20suffering%20among%20the%20people%20of%20Manipur%20but%20also%20have%20led%20to%20loss%20of%20several%20lives.%20The%20Executive%20Committee%20expresses%20its%20deep%20concern%20over%20the%20incidents%20which%20have%20tarnished%20the%20humanitarian%20ethics%20to%20its%20core.%20We%20categorically%20condemn%20the%20gender-based%20violence%20and%20humiliation%20as%20it%20has%20far-reaching%20consequences%20on%20the%20victims%E2%80%99%20physical%20and%20psychological%20well-being%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9C%5BWe%5D%20condemn%20the%20inaction%20of%20the%20state%20police%20in%20bringing%20the%20culprits%20to%20book%20for%20a%20long%20period%20of%20two%20months%20and%20their%20inability%20to%20generally%20tackle%20the%20debilitating%20violence%20in%20the%20State%20of%20Manipur%2C%E2%80%9Dthe%20apex%20court%20body%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SCBA%20has%20also%20urged%20the%20state%20and%20central%20governments%20to%20%E2%80%9Cimmediately%20take%20action%20to%20punish%20the%20perpetrators%20and%20prevent%20other%20acts%20of%20violence%20in%20the%20state%20which%20are%20still%20continuing%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Ftop-stories%2Fsupreme-court-bar-association-manipur-sexual-assault-video-condemns-inaction-state-police-arresting-culprits-233310%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELiveLaw%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20urged%20citizens%20to%20remain%20calm%20and%20respect%20one%20another%E2%80%99s%20rights%20and%20freedoms%20to%20maintain%20peace%20in%20the%20state%20%E2%80%9Cso%20that%20no%20such%20gruesome%20incident%20could%20be%20further%20reported%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20Talked%20About%20the%20Manipur%20Violence.%20But%20Did%20He%20Really%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fcommunalism%2Fmanipur-video-two-kuki-women-parade