s%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fmanipur-video-meitei-womens-group-sets-accused-mans-house-on-fire%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pak%20Board%20Unhappy%20Over%20Jay%20Shah's%20%5C%22Shock%5C%22%20Asia%20Cup%20Announcement%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20Cricket%20Board%20(PCB)%20has%20expressed%20its%20dissatisfaction%20over%20BCCI%20secretary%20and%20president%20of%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%2C%20Jay%20Shah%20announcing%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20upcoming%20Asia%20Cup%202023%20before%20its%20own%20official%20ceremony%20in%20Lahore%20earlier%20this%20week.%20The%20PCB%20had%20organised%20an%20event%20to%20announce%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20schedule%20along%20with%20unveiling%20the%20trophy%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2019%20evening%20in%20Lahore%2C%20which%20was%20attended%20by%20a%20few%20former%20Pakistan%20cricketers%20and%20PCB's%20Cricket%20Management%20Committee%20(CMC)%20headed%20by%20Zaka%20Ashraf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20half-an-hour%20before%20the%20start%20of%20the%20event%2C%20Shah%20announced%20the%20schedule%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BThe%20PCB%20had%20a%20clear%20understanding%20with%20the%20Asian%20Cricket%20Council%20(ACC)%20(that)%20it%20would%20release%20the%20schedule%20of%20the%20Asia%20Cup%2C%20five%20minutes%20after%20the%20ceremony%20started%20in%20Lahore.%20But%20unfortunately%2C%20half-an-hour%20before%20the%20ceremony%20started%20around%207.15%20P.M%2C%20Jay%20Shah%20had%20announced%20it%20on%20social%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20reliable%20source%20in%20the%20board%20told%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20said%20that%20the%20decision%20to%20announce%20the%20schedule%20by%20Jay%20Shah%20had%20spoilt%20the%20PCB's%20ceremony%2C%20which%20was%20held%20but%20lost%20its%20relevance%20as%20the%20schedule%20was%20already%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20source%20added%20that%20the%20PCB%20had%20conveyed%20its%20displeasure%20to%20the%20ACC%20over%20the%20incident%2C%20but%20was%20told%20it%20was%20all%20due%20to%20a%20misunderstanding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ACC's%20explanation%20was%20about%20misunderstandings%20over%20the%20time%20difference%20and%20all%20that%2C%20but%20the%20thing%20is%2C%20India%20is%20half-an-hour%20ahead%20of%20Pakistan%20time%2C%20so%20Jay%20Shah's%20announcement%20was%20a%20shock%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20source%20in%20the%20board%20said%20it%20appeared%20as%20if%20Shah%20had%20settled%20scores%20for%20the%20unprofessional%20manner%20in%20which%20the%20PCB%20chairman%20Ashraf%20and%20the%20sports%20minister%2C%20Ahsan%20Mazari%2C%20had%20handled%20the%20meeting%20held%20between%20Shah%20and%20Ashraf%20in%20Durban%20during%20the%20ICC%20annual%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20appears%20as%20if%20Jay%20Shah%20settled%20scores%20after%20the%20confusion%20and%20questions%20he%20had%20to%20face%20over%2C%20whether%20he%20had%20accepted%20an%20invitation%20from%20Zaka%20to%20visit%20Pakistan%20for%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20matches%20which%20was%20widely%20circulated%20by%20Mazari%20and%20the%20PCB%20in%20the%20media%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20source%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Asia%20Cup%20is%20scheduled%20to%20start%20on%20August%2030%20in%20Multan%20with%20the%20hosts%20Pakistan%20taking%20on%20Nepal%20in%20the%20tournament-opener.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20much-anticipated%20clash%20between%20India%20and%20Pakistan%2C%20who%20are%20placed%20in%20Group%20A%2C%20will%20be%20held%20in%20Kandy%20on%20September%202.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20will%20host%20four%20out%20of%20the%2013%20matches%20of%20Asia%20Cup%202013%20including%20the%20first%20Super%204s%20fixture%2C%20while%20the%20remaining%20nine%20matches%20including%20the%20final%20will%20be%20played%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from