mpUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22For%20Her%20Son's%20Graduation%2C%20Shefali%20Shah%20%5C%22Planned%20Very%20Nice%20Dinner%20But...%5C%22%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EShefali%20Shah%20is%20a%20proud%20mom%20and%20she%20shared%20her%20happy%20moment%20with%20her%20Instafam.%20The%20actor%20posted%20pictures%20from%20son%20Aryaman%20Shah's%20graduation%20ceremony%20and%20accompanied%20the%20photos%20with%20a%20lovely%20post.%20The%20album%20also%20features%20her%20husband%20and%20filmmaker%20Vipul%20Shah%20and%20their%20son%20Maurya.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fshefali-shah-reveals-she-was-touched-inappropriately-and-didnt-say-anything-everyones-gone-through-it-3935042%5C%22%3EShefali%20Shah%3C%2Fa%3E%20began%20her%20note%20with%20these%20words%2C%20%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20kids%20were%20babies%2C%20each%20moment%20was%20a%20new%20achievement.%20Their%20first%20flip%20over%20on%20their%20tummy%2C%20the%20first%20time%20they%20crawled%2C%20their%20first%20steps%2C%20first%20words.%20To%20the%20first%20time%20they%20tied%20their%20shoe%20laces.%20Many%20firsts%20and%20each%20one%20as%20special%20as%20the%20other.%20Then%20came%20the%20first%20day%20of%20toddlers%20school%2C%20fear%20rolling%20down%20through%20tears%20for%20them%20and%20me%2C%20then%20the%20colours%2C%20alphabets%2C%20poems%2C%20friends...%20with%20them%20I%20grew.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20as%20they%20grew%20older%20there%20weren't%20very%20many%20firsts%2C%20yet%20each%20grade%2C%20each%20goal%20scored%2C%20each%20medal%20won%2C%20each%20meal%20they%20cooked%2C%20each%20laundry%20they%20did%20was%20as%20important.%20One%20more%20step%20towards%20coming%20on%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShefali%20Shah%20added%20that%20she%20waited%20this%20moment%20for%20the%20longest%20time%20and%20that%20it%20was%20every%20bit%20worth%20the%20wait.%20She%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAnd%20here%20we%20are%20today%2C%20celebrating%20one%20of%20the%20most%20important%20and%20proud%20moments%20of%20a%20parents%20life%2C%20our%20sunshine%20boy's%20graduation.%20I%20don't%20know%20if%20it%20means%20as%20much%20to%20him%2C%20as%20it%20does%20to%20us.%20But%20as%20I%20saw%20him%20clean%20shaved%2C%20looking%20so%20handsome%20and%20royal%20in%20his%20robe%2C%20fiddling%20with%20the%20ill%20fitting%20graduation%20cap%2C%20seeming%20cool%20as%20a%20cucumber%20like%20it%20was%20no%20big%20deal...%20I%20realised%20I%20was%20crossing%20another%20milestone%20with%20him.%20Winning%20an%20accolade%20much%20more%20magnificent%20than%20any%20I%20have%20ever%20won.%20But%20our%20young%20man%20is%20still%20my%20little%20baby.%20He%20searched%20for%20us%20from%20the%20stage%2C%20smiled%20blushingly%20and%20took%20instructions%20from%20our%20gestures%20(across%20a%20hall%20filled%20with%20hundreds)%20to%20readjust%20his%20crown.%20Smiled%2C%20tipped%20his%20hat%2C%20shook%20hands%20with%20the%20chancellor%2C%20received%20his%20graduation%20certificate%20with%20pride%20and%20humility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%20I%20have%20waited%20for%20this%20day%20and%20dreamt%20of%20it%20innumerable%20times%20but%20to%20be%20there%20watching%20him%20sprout%20his%20wings%20I%20flew%20higher%20than%20I%20can%20ever%20explain%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20an%20excerpt%20from%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fdelhi-crime-2-review-perceptive-and-powerful-portrait-of-city-at-war-with-itself-4-stars-3288416%5C%22%3E%3Ci%3EDelhi%20Crime%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20star's%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20actress%20wrote%20about%20%26quot%3Bbursting%20with%20pride%20and%20joy%20that%20only%20my%20kids%20can%20bring%26quot%3B%20and%20she%20added%20how%20the%20family%20spent%20the%20day%20together%20after%20the%20milestone.%20%26quot%3BHe%20then%20showed%20us%20around%20his%20campus%2C%20library%2C%20classrooms%20his%20first%20accommodation%20with%20a%20common%20kitchen%20everything.%20We%20planned%20on%20going%20for%20a%20very%20nice%20celebratory%20dinner%20but%20by%20the%20time%20we%20did%20go%20everything%20had%20shut.%20We%20luckily%20found%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20wall%20take%20away%20pizza%20place%2C%20we%20stood%20together%20on%20the%20street%20in%20the%20square%20sharing%20the%20food.%20It%20couldn't%20have%20been%20a%20better%20celebration%20even%20if%20we%20tried.%20Because%20any%20moment%20no%20matter%20how%20special%20or%20ordinary%20becomes%20priceless%20and%20precious%20because%20of%20my%20babies%20and%20I%20truly%20truly%20feel%20blessed%20by%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Shefali%20Shah%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%20Shefali%20Shah's%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCu8oUCTo7qE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCu8oUCTo7qE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCu8oUCTo7qE%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E