3BIn%20the%20instant%20case%2C%20the%20allegations%20are%20serious.%20In%20my%20view%2C%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20allegations%2C%20no%20doubt%2C%20is%20one%20of%20the%20relevant%20considerations%20while%20considering%20bail%20applications%20but%20it%20is%20not%20the%20only%20test%20or%20the%20factor%20to%20decide%20the%20same.%20When%20the%20undertrial%20prisoners%20are%20detained%20in%20jail%20for%20an%20indefinite%20period%2C%20Article%2021%20(right%20to%20life%20and%20personal%20liberty)%20of%20the%20Constitution%20is%20violated.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIn%20the%20matter%20at%20hand%2C%20in%20my%20considered%20opinion%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%20no%20purpose%20will%20be%20served%20by%20taking%20the%20accused%20persons%20in%20custody%2C%20at%20this%20stage%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20Mr%20Singh%20and%20Mr%20Tomar%20were%20accused%20of%20sexual%20assault%2C%20which%20carried%20a%20maximum%20punishment%20of%20seven%20years%20imprisonment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20further%20noted%20that%20the%20accused%20were%20not%20arrested%20during%20the%20investigation%20and%20as%20per%20the%20police%20report%2C%20they%20cooperated%20in%20the%20investigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20no%20stage%2C%20the%20Investigating%20Agency%2C%20speaking%20through%20the%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%2C%20has%20expressed%20its%20apprehension%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20are%20abusing%20their%20positions%20or%20are%20making%20attempts%20to%20tamper%20with%20evidence%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20been%20conveyed%20is%20that%20sufficient%20conditions%20must%20be%20imposed%20to%20the%20extent%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20do%20not%2C%20directly%20or%20indirectly%2C%20approach%20the%20victims%20to%20influence%20them%2C%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Additional%20Public%20Prosecutor%20has%20not%20even%20opposed%20the%20bail%2C%20his%20simple%20submission%20is%20that%20it%20must%20be%20decided%20in%20accordance%20with%20directions%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20noted%20that%20counsel%20for%20the%20complainants%2C%20upon%20being%20asked%2C%20has%20not%20placed%20on%20record%20any%20specific%20instance%20where%20the%20victims%20were%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20counsel%20has%20expressed%20his%20apprehension%20that%20the%20accused%20persons%20may%20approach%20the%20victims%20and%20may%20try%20to%20influence%20them%20in%20future%2C%20however%2C%20the%20present%20entails%20no%20such%20detail%2C%20the%20judge%20further%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20law%20of%20the%20land%20is%20equal%20for%20all%2C%20it%20can%20neither%20be%20pulled%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20victims%20nor%20can%20it%20tilt%20in%20the%20favour%20of%20the%20accused%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20directed%20that%20the%20accused%20shall%20not%20tamper%20with%20any%20evidence%2C%20or%20make%20any%20threat%2C%20inducement%20or%20promise%20to%20any%20victim%20or%20any%20other%20witnesses%20in%20any%20manner%20whatsoever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20accused%20persons%20shall%20attend%20the%20court%20whenever%20called.%20The%20accused%20persons%20shall%20not%20commit%20any%20similar%20crimes%2C%20of%20which%20they%20are%20suspected.%20The%20accused%20persons%20shall%20not%20leave%20the%20country%20without%20the%20prior%20permission%20of%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20directed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20Police%20had%20filed%20a%20charge%20sheet%20against%20the%20six-time%20MP%20on%20June%2015%20under%20sections%20354%20(assault%20or%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20outrage%20her%20modesty)%2C%20354A%20(sexual%20harassment)%2C%20354D%20(stalking)%20and%20506%20(criminal%20intimidation)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20(IPC).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20h