e%20judge%20apparently%20faced%20some%20inconvenience.%20The%20letter%20said%20that%C2%A0Justice%20Chowdhary%20sought%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20general%20manager%20of%20the%20North%20Central%20Railway%2C%20Prayagraj%2C%20for%20his%20poor%20experience%20on%20the%20first-class%20AC%20coach%20of%20the%20Purushotam%20Express%20from%20New%20Delhi%20to%20Prayagraj.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20was%20late%20by%20more%20than%203%20hours%20and%20there%20were%20no%20government%20railway%20police%20(GRP)%20officers%20in%20the%20coach%20to%20meet%20the%20judge%E2%80%99s%20requirements%20despite%20%E2%80%9Crepeated%20intimation%E2%80%9D.%20Pantry%20car%20workers%20also%20did%20not%20attend%20to%20the%20judge%20to%20provide%20refreshments%20and%20the%20pantry%20car%20manager%20did%20not%20answer%20calls%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livelaw.in%2Fnews-updates%2Fallahabad-high-court-judge-railway-officials-explanation-inconvenience-train-journey-justice-gautam-chowdhary-233039%5C%22%3Ethe%20letter%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20which%20was%20shared%20widely%20on%20social%20media%2C%20raised%20concerns%20among%20the%20public%20about%20the%20sense%20of%20entitlement%20among%20members%20of%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20wrote%20to%20the%20chief%20justices%20of%20all%20the%20high%20courts%20and%20expressed%20displeasure%20over%20the%20incident.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fcji-expresses-displeasure-over-explanation-sought-by-allahabad-high-court-judge-for-bad-train-journey%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said%20that%20the%20letter%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20%E2%80%9Cjustifiable%E2%80%9D%20criticism%20of%20the%20judiciary.%20Judges%20must%20ensure%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprotocol%20facilities%E2%80%9D%20that%20they%20get%20due%20to%20their%20position%20must%20not%20be%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmanifestation%20of%20power%20and%20authority%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20communication%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20justifiable%20disquiet%20both%20within%20and%20outside%20the%20Judiciary.%20Protocol%20%E2%80%98facilities%E2%80%99%20which%20are%20made%20available%20to%20Judges%20should%20not%20be%20utilised%20to%20assert%20a%20claim%20to%20privilege%20which%20sets%20them%20apart%20from%20society%20or%20as%20a%20manifestation%20of%20power%20or%20authority%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20letter%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20asked%20judges%20to%20exercise%20judicial%20authority%20wisely%2C%20both%20on%C2%A0and%20off%20the%20bench%20because%20it%20%E2%80%9Csustains%20the%20credibility%20and%20legitimacy%20of%20the%20judiciary%20and%20the%20confidence%20which%20society%20has%20in%20judges%E2%80%9D.%20CJI%20Chandrachud%20said%20there%20should%20be%20self-reflection%20and%20counselling%20within%20the%20judiciary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CProtocol%20facilities%20which%20are%20made%20available%20to%20judges%20should%20not%20be%20used%20in%20a%20manner%20that%20is%20liable%20to%20result%20in%20inconvenience%20to%20others%20or%20to%20bring%20public%20criticism%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%E2%80%9D%20his%20letter%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EBar%20and%20Bench%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20letter%20sent%20by%20the%20Allahabad%20high%20court%2C%20the%20CJI%20noted%20that%20judges%20do%20not%20possess%20disciplinary%20jurisdiction%20over%20railway%20personnel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHence%20there%20was%20no%20occasion%20for%20an%20officer%20of%20the%20(Allahabad)%20High%20Court%20to%20call%20for%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20railway%20personnel%20%E2%80%98to%20be%20placed%20before%20his%20lordship%20for%20his%20kind%20perusal.%E2%80%99%20Evidently%2C%20the%20officer%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20was%20carrying%20out%20a%20direction%20of%20the%20Judge%20of%20the%20High%20Court%20in%20this%20instance%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20CJI%E2%80%99s%20l