try%20of%20External%20Affairs%20has%20informed%20parliament%20that%20Rs%20254.87%20crore%20has%20been%20spent%20on%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20trips%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20written%20question%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20MP%20Sanjay%20Singh%2C%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20external%20affairs%20V.%20Muraleedharan%20said%20on%20Thursday%2C%20July%2020%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20information%20available%2C%20the%20expenditure%20on%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20visit%20during%20the%20last%20five%20years%20is%20Rs%202%2C54%2C87%2C01%2C373.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20the%20ministry%20had%20in%20response%20to%20a%20written%20question%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20the%20expenditure%20on%20foreign%20trips%20by%20the%20president%2C%20prime%20minister%20and%20external%20affairs%20minister%20said%20that%20Rs%2022%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20trips%20between%2021%20February%202019%20to%2016%20November%202022.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGOI%20incurred%20an%20amount%20of%20INR%206%2C24%2C31%2C424%20for%20President%E2%80%99s%20visits%2C%20an%20amount%20of%20INR%2022%2C76%2C76%2C934%20for%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20visits%20and%20an%20amount%20of%20INR%2020%2C87%2C01%2C475%20for%20External%20Affairs%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20visits%20abroad%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20reply%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20written%20reply%20also%20included%20a%20list%20of%2021%20countries%20that%20Modi%20had%20visited%20during%20this%20period.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20in%20a%20separate%20reply%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20also%20said%20that%20an%20expenditure%20of%20over%20Rs%2030%20crore%20has%20been%20incurred%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20trips%20between%20February%202021%20to%20June%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20response%20to%20a%20written%20question%20by%20CPI(M)%20MP%20V.%20Sivadasan%2C%20Muraleedharan%20said%3A%20%E2%80%9CAs%20per%20information%20available%2C%20the%20expenditure%20on%20Prime%20Minister%E2%80%99s%20overseas%20visit%20from%20February%202021%20till%20June%202023%20is%20Rs.%2030%2C80%2C47%2C075%2F-.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20reply%20also%20lists%2020%20overseas%20trips%20by%20the%20prime%20minister%20during%20this%20period%2C%20beginning%20with%20his%20trip%20to%20Bangladesh%20between%20March%2026-27%2C%202021%20to%20his%20visits%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Egypt%20between%20June%2020-25%202023.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20statements%20seem%20to%20suggest%20that%20between%20%3Cspan%3EFebruary%202019%20and%20June%202023%2C%20roughly%20Rs%2050%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20tours.%20However%2C%20the%20response%20to%20the%20question%20on%20the%20expenditure%20during%20the%20past%20five%20years%20places%20it%20more%20than%20Rs%20200%20crore%20more%20%E2%80%93%20at%20Rs%20254%20crore.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20written%20to%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20about%20the%20figures.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20a%20statement%20by%20then%20minister%20of%20state%20for%20external%20affairs%20V.K.%20Singh%20given%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20July%2019%2C%202018%2C%20a%20sum%20of%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmea-rti-modi-foreign-visits%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ERs%201%2C484%20crore%20was%20spent%20on%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20trips%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20June%2015%2C%202014%20and%20June%2010%2C%202018.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20details%20available%20on%20the%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fen%2Fdetails-of-foreigndomestic-visits%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EPM%20India%20website%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20Modi%20has%20been%20on%2071%20foreign%20trips%20since%20he%20first%20became%20Prime%20Minister%20in%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20website%20lists%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20visits%20%E2%80%93%20from%20his%20first%20to%20Bhutan%20in%20June%202014%20to%20his%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20and%20Egypt%20last%20month.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ESince%20then%20Modi%20has%20visited%20France%20and%20the%20UAE%20this%20month.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20figures%20available%20on%20the%20PM%20India%20website%2C%20in%20comparison%2C%20former%20prime%20minister%20Manmohan%20Singh%20visited%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pmindia.gov.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F02%2Fformer-PM-Manmohan-Singh-Visit-02.02.2016.pdf%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E73%20countries%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20during%20his%20tenure%20between%20May%202004%20to%20May%202014.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20frequent%20foreign%20trips%20have%20been%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fwhat-does-country-gain-from-pm-modis-foreign-visits-congress-asks%2Farticleshow%2F49076216.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Equestioned%20by%20the%20opposition%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20the%20last%20nine%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20recent%20months%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20foreign%20trips%20have%20also%20been%20raked%20up%20by%20the%20opposition%20to%20ask%20questions%20about%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fmagic-happened-after-2014-rahul-gandhi-questions-surge-in-adanis-fortunes-under-modi-2%2F1360018%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehow%20many%20times%20Gautam%20Adani%20accompanied%20Modi%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20on%20these%20trips.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20questions%20came%20on%