.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20A%20horrifying%20video%20of%20her%20sexual%20assault%20by%20a%20mob%20of%20men%20belonging%20to%20Manipur%E2%80%99s%20Meitei%20community%20has%20gone%20viral%20two%20days%20ago.%20She%20is%20aware%20of%20its%20impact%20in%20faraway%20mainland%20India%20%E2%80%93%20national%20outrage%2C%20and%20the%20prime%20minister%20finally%20breaking%20his%20silence%20on%20the%20violence%20that%20has%20been%20going%20on%20in%20her%20state%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20life%20must%20go%20on.%20On%20the%20morning%20of%20July%2021%20when%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20caught%20up%20with%20her%2C%20she%20was%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20preparing%20a%20meal%20for%20her%20family.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20a%20four%20year-old-child%2C%20you%20see%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20this%20correspondent.%20Nearly%20three%20months%20ago%2C%20it%20was%20on%20behalf%20of%20that%20child%20that%20she%20pleaded%20her%20sexual%20assaulters%20to%20show%20some%20mercy%2C%20to%20not%20take%20her%20life.%20She%20recalled%2C%20%E2%80%9CThey%20then%20ordered%20me%2C%20remove%20your%20clothes%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20get%20killed%20by%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExcerpts%20from%20a%20telephonic%20interview%20with%20the%2044-year-old%20survivor%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECan%20you%20recall%20what%20happened%20to%20you%20and%20your%20family%20on%20May%204%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYes%3B%20on%20that%20morning%2C%20we%20were%20warned%20by%20some%20Meitei%20neighbours%20about%20a%20Meitei%20mob%20heading%20our%20way%2C%20to%20our%20village%2C%20B.%20Phainom%20(in%20Kangpokpi%20district).%20They%20told%20us%20to%20flee.%20Several%20fled%20to%20the%20jungles%3B%20I%20sent%20my%20child%20with%20some%20Kuki%20women%20from%20the%20village.%20As%20me%20and%20my%20husband%20were%20preparing%20to%20leave%20the%20village%2C%20the%20mob%20arrived%20and%20surrounded%20us.%20While%20he%20was%20taken%20away%20to%20a%20different%20side%20along%20with%20some%20other%20Kuki%20villagers%2C%20I%20was%20herded%20in%20another%20direction.%20We%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20awaited%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20from%20within%20the%20mob%20told%20the%20women%20that%20your%20community%20had%20raped%20our%20%5BMeitei%5D%20women%20in%20Churachandpur%20%5Bthat%20contention%20was%20based%20on%20a%20fake%20video%5D%2C%20so%20we%20will%20do%20the%20same%20to%20you%20now.%20The%20father%20and%20the%20son%20of%20the%20youngest%20woman%20among%20us%20resisted%20and%20were%20soon%20killed%20by%20the%20mob.%20I%20pleaded%20with%20them%20saying%20I%20have%20a%20child%2C%20don%E2%80%99t%20kill%20me.%20They%20told%20us%2C%20then%20remove%20your%20clothes%20if%20you%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20get%20killed%3B%20if%20we%20didn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%2C%20they%20would%20have%20killed%20us%20too%3B%20we%20had%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20follow%20their%20diktat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happened%20next%3F%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20we%20removed%20our%20clothes%2C%20some%20men%20held%20us%20and%20began%20parading%20us%20naked.%20The%20mob%20was%20of%20about%20a%20thousand%20people.%20My%20private%20parts%20were%20touched%3B%20fingers%20were%20put%20into%20my%20vagina%3B%20some%20%5Bpeople%5D%20put%20their%20tongue%20into%20my%20mouth.%20We%20were%20being%20dragged%20to%20a%20paddy%20field%20nearby.%20I%20continued%20to%20plead%20with%20them%20to%20leave%20me%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20my%20child.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-imphal-violence-daughters-killed%5C%22%3EOur%20Daughters%20Were%20Killed%20in%20Imphal%20on%20May%205.%20We%20Haven%E2%80%99t%20Even%20Been%20Able%20to%20Retrieve%20Their%20Bodies.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20escape%20from%20the%20scene%20eventually%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20with%20the%20help%20of%20some%20local%20Meitei%20men.%20They%20intervened%20and%20gave%20their%20shirts%20to%20us%20to%20wear%3B%20they%20told%20us%20to%20leave%20the%20scene%20at%20once.%20While%20we%20were%20walking%20past%2C%20we%20were%20sneered%20at%20by%20some%20men%2C%20saying%20look%20at%20these%20tribal%20women%20wearing%20men%E2%80%99s%20clothes.%20Some%20more%20Meitei%20men%20intervened%20and%20asked%20us%20where%20are%20our%20clothes%3B%20they%20helped%20us%20pick%20up%20our%20clothes%20from%20the%20roadside.%20The%20youngest%20among%20us%2C%20whose%20father%20and%20son%20were%20killed%20before%20our%20eyes%20because%20they%20tried%20to%20protect%20her%20dignity%2C%20wanted%20to%20go%20near%20their%20bodies.%20I%20tried%20helping%20her%20but%20we%20were%20strictly%20told%2C%20if%20we%20try%20to%20go%20near%20the%20bodies%2C%20we%20will%20be%20killed%20too.%20I%20then%20pleaded%20with%20her%3B%20let%E2%80%99s%20save%20our%20lives%3B%20they%20are%20anyway%20dead.%20I%20dragged%20her%20from%20the%20scene%20while%20the%20bodies%20remained%20on%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cstrong%3E%20also%20spoke%20to%20the%20survivor%E2%80%99s%20husband.%20Excerpts%20from%20the%20interview%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20were%20you%20when%20she%20was%20sexually%20assaulted%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20mentioned%20earlier%2C%20I%20was%20herded%20in%20a%20different%20direction%20by%20the%20mob.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20you%20survive%20the%20killer%20mob%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20sheer%20luck!%20Among%20the%20thousand-strong%20mob%20were%20some%20boys%20whose%20fathers%20and%20I%20are%20friends.%20I%20am%20also%20the%20village%20head.%20They%20recognised%20me%20and%20told%20the%20others%20that%20they%20were%20taking%20me%20to%20another%20side%2C%20and%20when%20we%20were%20out%20of%20sight%20from%20the%20rest%2C%20they%20told%20me%20to%20flee.%20That%E2%80%99s%20how%20I%20saved%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20filed%20the%20FIR%20at%20Saikul%20police%20station%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20did%2C%20on%20May%2018%2C%20two%20weeks%20later.%20My%20nearest%20police%20station%20is%20Nongpuk%20Sekmai%20but%20I%20was%20so%20scared%20to%20go%20there%20after%20the%20assault.%20Therefore%2C%20after%20reuniting%20with%20my%20wife%20and%20child%20in%20the%20jungle%20where%20we%20originally%20intended%20to%20flee%20to%2C%20we%20started%20off%20towards%20Khamjong%20district%2C%20and%20were%20hosted%20by%20a%20Thangkhul%20Naga%20family%20at%20Lairam%20Khullen%20village%20for%20a%20week.%20I%20am%20most%20grateful%20to%20them%20for%20that%20gesture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20we%20moved%20to%20Tengnoupal%20district%20wherefrom%20I%20could%20send%20my%20family%20to%20a%20relief%20camp%20in%20Churachandpur%3B%20my%20wife%20belongs%20to%20that%20district.%20Once%20I%20was%20sure%20that%20they%20were%20safe%2C%20I%20headed%20to%20Kangpokpi%20district%20where%20I%20come%20from%2C%20and%20eventually%20could%20go%20to%20Saikul%20police%20station%20to%20lodge%20the%20FIR%20on%20May%2018.%20But%20nothing%20happened%20till%20the%20videos%20went%20viral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%20have%20served%20in%20the%20Indian%20Army%3B%20how%20do%20you%20see%20this%20personal%20tragedy%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20fought%20the%20Kargil%20war%2C%20fought%20for%20my%20country%E2%80%99s%20honour%2C%20but%20that%20day%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20save%20the%20honour%20of%20my%20wife%20from%20a%20killer%20mob%20within%20my%20own%20country.%20I%20feel%20short%20of%20words%20to%20express%20what%20I%20feel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAfter%20over%20two%20months%20passed%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%20eventually%20spoke%20on%20the%20Manipur%20violence%20because%20the%20video%20went%20viral.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EI%20don%E2%80%99t%20understand%20politics%3B%20I%20served%20my%20country.%20All%20I%20want%20to%20tell%20the%20prime%20minister%20is%2C%20give%20the%20women%20justice.%20Give%20us%20justice.%20After%20taking%20retirement%20from%20the%20army%2C%20I%20had%20set%20up%20a%20small%20business%20in%20my%20village%20and%20bought%20a%20mini%20truck%20with%20the%20money%20I%20had%20got%20on%20retirement.%20Today%2C%20my%20house%20is%20gone%3B%20my%20mini%20truck%20stands%20next%20to%20it%2C%20burnt%20down.%20The%20machine%20I%20had%20bought%20to%20carry%20out%20a%20small%20business%20from%20home%20was%20looted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20here%20I%20am%2C%20standing%20with%20my%20wife%2C%20with%20all%20the%20victims%20of%20this%20conflict%2C%20of%20mob%20attack.%20I%20thank%20everyone%20who%20has%20helped%20bring%20these%20horrific%20attacks%20to%20light.%20All%20I%20plead%20for%20is%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689922209000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F21121708%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-20-at-9.41.48-PM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fkuki-woman-from-viral-video-speaks-out-on-sexual-assault-witnessing-murders%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Her%20husband%2C%20who%20served%20in%20the%20army%2C%20talks%20about%20his%20sadness%20at%20being%20unable%20to%20protect%20his%20wife%20and%20people%2C%20and%20how%20he%20escaped%20from%20a%20mob.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fwomen%2Fkuki-woman-from-viral-video-speaks-out-on-sexual-assault-witnessing-murders%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Australian%20sailor%20gives%20up%20dog%20who%20helped%20him%20survive%20at%20sea%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689921780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F07%2F768x432%2Fskynews-timothy-shaddock-australian-sailor_6225328.jpg%3F20230721084744%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Faustralian-sailor-lost-at-sea