)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3EGautam%20Trivedi%20(26)%2C%20a%20Vadodara%20resident%20and%20music%20producer%20by%20profession%2C%20wanted%20to%20grow%20his%20own%20vegetables.%20After%20receiving%20training%20from%20Shashank%2C%20he%20set%20up%20an%20aquaponics%20farm%20in%20a%2050%20sq%20ft%20area%20of%20his%20garden.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20an%20aquaponics%20set%20up%2C%20we%20get%20nice%20green%20leafy%20vegetables%20that%20are%20crunchier%20and%20better%20in%20taste%20than%20that%20available%20in%20the%20market.%20It%20also%20requires%20low%20maintenance%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20trained%2035%20people%20from%20Gujarat%20and%20Rajasthan%20through%20offline%20and%20online%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20one-to-one%20process.%20I%20conduct%20a%20six-hour%20class.%20In%20the%20initial%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20inform%20them%20about%20the%20different%20plants%20that%20a%20farmer%20can%20grow.%20In%20the%20next%20three%20hours%2C%20I%20train%20them%20on%20how%20to%20implement%20the%20aquaponics%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Shashank%2C%20who%20charges%20Rs%202%2C500%20and%20Rs%203%2C000%20for%20offline%20and%20online%20classes%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharing%20a%20few%20tips%20on%20aquaponics%20farming%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CCrops%20require%20an%20environment%20with%20the%20optimal%20temperature.%20For%20instance%2C%20to%20grow%20leafy%20vegetables%2C%20a%20temperature%20between%2025%20and%2030%20degrees%20Celsius%20is%20needed.%20Whereas%20for%20hilly%20crops%2C%20such%20as%20strawberries%2C%20you%20need%20to%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20to%2018%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20and%20for%20crops%20like%20lettuce%2C%20up%20to%2015%20degrees%20Celsius.%20We%20use%20urban%20clay%20pots%20to%20regulate%20the%20temperature%20of%20water%20in%20the%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(m