chocolates%20and%20decided%20to%20take%20a%20leap%20of%20faith%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20in%20the%20business%20for%20only%20a%20few%20months%2C%20he%20was%20a%20little%20sceptical%20about%20this%20move.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20do%20something%20about%20the%20situation.%20I%20did%20not%20want%20to%20lose%20such%20a%20great%20variety%20of%20fruits%20and%20also%20wanted%20to%20put%20them%20on%20a%20global%20map.%20I%20just%20wanted%20to%20tell%20people%20that%20%E2%80%98Hey!%20These%20fruits%20exist%20and%20I%20have%20put%20them%20in%20chocolate%20for%20you%20to%20try%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Co-founders%20of%20Saraam%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fsaraam-1-1689164612-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323577%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ECo-founders%20of%20Saraam.%20Picture%20credit%3A%20Digvijay%20Singh%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20started%20out%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F294695%2Fhealth-benefits-of-ber-indian