nal%20laundry%20service.%20Sure%2C%20dry%20cleaners%20existed%2C%20but%20there%20were%20no%20laundromats%2C%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201707px)%20100vw%2C%201707px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221707%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Laundry%20being%20processed%20at%20a%20Uclean%20Store%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-scaled.jpg%201707w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-500x750.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-768x1152.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-1024x1536.jpg%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-1365x2048.jpg%201365w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FDSC07710-min-1688998840-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-323275%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EA%20dress%20is%20being%20folded%20at%20a%20UClean%20store.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20her%20husband%20Arunabh%20Sinha%20was%20heading%20the%20North%20India%20business%20of%20a%20budget%20hotel%20chain.%20While%20helping%20them%20expand%20their%20business%20in%20North%20India%2C%20Arunabh%20found%20that%20the%20biggest%20problem%20they%20were%20facing%20across%20the%20country%20was%20laundry%20related.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20would%20get%20complaints%20daily%20regarding%20dirty%20bed%20sheets%2C%20towels%2C%20and%20clothes.%20The%20laundry%20service%20was%20not%20good%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh%2C%20an%20IIT-Bombay%20alumnus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%20with%20these%20facts%2C%20the%20couple%20started%20thinking%20of%20launching%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320745%2Fwoman-scientist-methane-greenhouse-gas-help-farmers-string-bio-startup-ezhil-subbian%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20I%20looked%20for%20a%20solution%20to%20the%20laundry%20problem%20in%20the%20hotel%2C%20I%20started%20researching%20the%20market.%20I%20found%20that%20the%20industry%20was%20unorganised%2C%20and%20there%20were%20no%20professional%20players%20other%20than%20our%20neighbourhood%20%3Cem%3Edhobis%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20RedSeer%E2%80%99s%20research%20report%20%3Cem%3EIndia%20Laundry%20Services%20Market%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20laundry%20market%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20to%20%2415%20billion%20by%202025%E2%80%9D.%20Out%20of%20this%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20is%20less%20than%20five%20percent%20of%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20take%20up%20the%20opportunity%20to%20organise%20the%20laundry%20industry%20and%20offer%20%E2%80%98quality%20and%20consistent%20services%E2%80%99.%20Arunabh%20quit%20his%20job%20in%20August%202016%2C%20and%20they%20launched%20a%20laundromat%20service%20called%20UClean%20in%20January%202017%20with%20a%20capital%20of%20Rs%2020%20lakh%2C%20which%20has%20grown%20to%20a%20Rs%20100%20crore%20business%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ECreating%20microentrepreneurs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FUn