r%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321740%2Fmother-daughters-dea-ojasvi-hema-sharma-chilzo-mumbai-global-cuisines-sauces-condiments%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elaundry%20industry%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20early%202010s%2C%20but%20logistics%20remained%20a%20major%20problem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMost%20of%20these%20laundry%20businesses%20operated%20through%20a%20hub%20and%20spoke%20model.%20They%20had%20their%20factories%20far%20away%20and%20logistics%20ate%20up%20their%20margins.%20Customers%20also%20complained%20about%20delays%20in%20the%20delivery%20of%20laundry.%20There%20was%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20transparency%20and%20trust.%20But%20even%20with%20these%20issues%2C%20people%20were%20giving%20their%20clothes%2C%20which%20showed%20us%20that%20the%20demand%20was%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Gunjan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20they%20decided%20to%20go%20the%20franchise%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20launched%20a%20live%20laundry%20model%20where%20everything%20is%20handled%20hyperlocal.%20Anybody%20can%20visit%20our%20laundromats%20and%20see%20our%20machines%2C%20irons%20and%20detergents%20that%20are%20being%20used.%20You%20can%20see%20how%20your%20clothes%20are%20washed.%20The%20customer%20deserves%20to%20know%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arunabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20every%20neighbourhood%20is%20different%20in%20India%2C%20they%20decided%20to%20work%20with%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCtrJtxTO8qj%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20UClean%20(%40_uclean_)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDynamics%20change%20every%2030%20km.%20We%20would%20have%20to%20customise%20for%20every%20neighbourhood.%20So%20we%20developed%20a%20strategy%20that%20would%20work%20everywhere%20%E2%80%94%20working%20with%20local%20players.%20They%20know%20their%20locale%20well%20and%20what%20people%20want.%20This%20way%2C%20we%20are%20also%20creating%20micro-entrepreneurs%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20says%20that%20they%20structured%20an%20existing%20need%20and%20focused%20on%20delivering%20quality.%20They%20knew%20that%20laundry%20is%20an%20essential%20service%20and%20many%20need%20help%20with%20it.%20By%20offering%20a%20simple%2C%20daily%20service%2C%20they%E2%80%99re%20earning%20in%20crores.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20most%20popular%20service%20is%20%E2%80%98Laundry%20by%20Kg%E2%80%99%20where%20you%20can%20get%20your%20clothes%20%E2%80%98washed%20and%20folded%E2%80%99%20or%20%E2%80%98washed%20and%20ironed%E2%80%99.%20They%20also%20offer%20steam%20ironing%2C%20dry%20cleaning%2C%20shoe%2C%20carpet%2C%20sofa%20and%20bag%20cleaning%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20UClean%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferre